0player%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22315%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%20data-mce-type%3D%5C%22bookmark%5C%22%3E%EF%BB%BF%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20a%2035-minute%20interview%20to%20Karan%20Thapar%20for%20The%20Wire%2C%20Ramachandra%20Guha%2C%20who%20is%20not%20just%20a%20friend%20and%20admirer%20of%20Bishan%20Singh%20Bedi%20but%20an%20historian%20and%20author%20who%20has%20written%20compellingly%20on%20cricket%2C%20spoke%20at%20length%20about%C2%A0%20Bedi%E2%80%99s%20commitment%20and%20even%20calling%2C%20things%20he%20wrote%20and%20said%20and%20courageously%20stood%20up%20for%2C%20which%20many%20are%20not%20aware%20of.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAs%20a%20young%20cricketer%20Bedi%20%E2%80%9Cwas%20the%20most%20courageous%2C%20most%20direct%20and%20most%20forthright%20in%20fighting%20for%20cricketers%E2%80%99%20rights%E2%80%9D%20and%20this%20is%20something%20for%20which%20Guha%20says%20%E2%80%9Che%20paid%20a%20price%E2%80%9D.%20After%20retirement%2C%20Bedi%20%E2%80%9Ceschewed%20lucrative%20commentary%20contracts%20to%20nurture%20and%20mentor%20young%20cricketers%20in%20the%20coaching%20camps%20he%20ran%E2%80%9D.%20As%20a%20result%2C%20he%20forsook%20the%20huge%20sums%20of%20money%20others%20like%20Sunil%20Gavaskar%20and%20Ravi%20Shastri%20have%20earned%20from%20cricket%20commentary.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EYoung%20cricketers%2C%20particularly%20those%20from%20the%20%E2%80%9Cmofussil%E2%80%9D%2C%20would%20often%20stay%20in%20Bedi%E2%80%99s%20home.%20On%20an%20occasion%20when%20the%20Indian%20cricket%20team%20and%20the%20Indian%20hockey%20team%20were%20in%20Bangalore%20at%20the%20same%20time%20and%20Bedi%20noticed%20that%20whilst%20the%20cricketers%20were%20in%205-star%20hotels%20the%20hockey%20team%20was%20put%20up%20in%20a%20modest%20dormitory%20in%20the%20Kanteerava%20Stadium.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EGuha%20says%3A%20%E2%80%9CBedi%2C%20perhaps%20the%20only%20Indian%20cricketer%20who%20would%20have%20recognized%20the%20injustice%20of%20it%20all%2C%20took%20them%20out%20for%20dinner%2C%20I%20believe%20more%20than%20once.%E2%80%9D%20Ten%20years%20later%2C%20when%20the%20hockey%20player%20Surjit%20Singh%20died%20in%20a%20road%20accident%2C%20Bedi%20quietly%20donated%20some%20of%20the%20proceeds%20from%20his%20benefit%20match%20to%20the%20hockey%20player%E2%80%99s%20family.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThis%20is%20a%20side%20of%20Bedi%20no%20one%20knew%20of%20until%20Guha%20brought%20it%20to%20the%20world%E2%80%99s%20attention.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ELet%20me%20make%20one%20more%20point.%20This%20time%20about%20Bishan%20Singh%20Bedi%E2%80%99s%20boldness%20in%20commenting%20on%20and%20criticising%20politicians%2C%20including%20the%20present%20Prime%20Minister.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EFirst%2C%20however%2C%20this%20is%20what%20Ramachandra%20Guha%20says%20of%20cricketers%20today%3A%20%E2%80%9CIt%20is%20one%20of%20the%20sad%20truths%20about%20Indian%20cricket%20today%20that%20the%20greater%20the%20cricketer%2C%20the%20more%20opportunistic%20and%20spineless%20the%20human%20being.%20Cricketers%20with%20fame%20and%20wealth%20always%20seek%20to%20stay%20on%20the%20right%20side%20of%20the%20administrators%20of%20the%20Board%20of%20Control%20for%20Cricket%20in%20India%2C%20always%20curry%20favour%20with%20politicians%2C%20and%20never%20take%20a%20stand%20on%20matters%20of%20personal%20ethics%20or%20political%20principle.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EBedi%2C%20in%20contrast%2C%20truly%20stands%20out%20because%20he%20spoke%20his%20mind%2C%20repeatedly%2C%20forthrightly%20and%20unconcerned%20about%20the%20consequence.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1698918364000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F02151308%2Fkt-ram-b.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fvideo%2Fvideo-bishan-singh-bedi-karan-thapar-ramachandra-guha%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22'Bishan%20Singh%20Bedi%20stands%20out%20because%20he%20spoke%20his%20mind%2C%20repeatedly%2C%20forthrightly%20and%20unconcerned%20about%20the%20consequence.'%22%2C%22auth