%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22The%20UK%20AI%20summit's%20narrow%20focus%20on%20safety%20and%20existential%20risk%20means%20the%20real%20issues%20are%20being%20ignored%2C%20an%20AI%20ethicist%20says%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223710%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22UK%20Prime%20Minister%20Rishi%20Sunak.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F64ce360ef5d4870019e25311%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222473%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ESeveral%20groups%20have%20criticized%20the%20UK%20government's%20overemphasis%20on%20some%20of%20the%20more%20existential%20risks%20of%20AI.%3Cp%3ERichard%20Pohle%2FWPA%20Pool%20via%20Getty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20UK's%20AI%20safety%20summit%20kicks%20off%20on%20Wednesday.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3ESome%20have%20already%20slammed%20the%20event%20for%20ignoring%20several%20key%20issues.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3ESeveral%20groups%20have%20criticized%20the%20UK%20government's%20focus%20on%20the%20existential%20risks%20of%20AI.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20UK's%20AI%20safety%20summit%20kicked%20off%20on%20Wednesday%2C%20but%20the%20event%20is%20already%20surrounded%20by%20criticism.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESeveral%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ft.com%2Fcontent%2F07669dbf-a2b5-4472-943f-6ee1ba5a8336%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Egroups%20have%20criticized%3C%2Fa%3E%20the%20UK%20government's%20emphasis%20on%20some%20of%20the%20more%20existential%20risks%20of%20AI%2C%20sidelining%20other%20and%20perhaps%20more%20pressing%20concerns.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMerve%20Hickok%2C%20the%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Epresident%20of%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.caidp.org%2Fabout-2%2Fteam%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ECenter%20for%20AI%20and%20Digital%20Policy%2C%20told%20Insider%20%3C%2Fa%3Ethe%20summit%20began%20with%20a%20shared%20commitment%20with%20the%20US%20to%20work%20together%20for%20democratic%20AI%20values.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThen%20somehow%2C%20after%20the%20Prime%20Minister's%20meetings%20with%20tech%20companies%2C%20it%20started%20focusing%20narrowly%20only%20on%20the%20existential%20crisis%20as%20defined%20by%20AGI%20taking%20over%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENot%20only%20has%20the%20focus%20been%20narrowed%2C%20she%20added%2C%20but%20the%20people%20at%20the%20table%20are%20mostly%20major%20tech%20companies.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BCivil%20society%20and%20other%20voices%20and%20communities%20are%20sidelined%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%20%26quot%3BAlso%2C%20all%20the%20concerns%20about%20existing%20AI%20systems%20which%20are%20impacting%20our%20fundamental%20rights%20are%20sidelined%20as%20well.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHickok%20is%20not%20the%20only%20one%20to%20raise%20concerns%20about%20the%20current%20rhetoric%20around%20AI%20safety.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETwo%20leading%20experts%20have%20dismissed%20existential%20threats%20and%20some%20of%20the%20doomsday%20scenarios.%20Both%20have%20suggested%20big%20tech%20companies%20might%20have%20something%20to%20gain%20from%20inflating%20the%20more%20dramatic%20fears%20around%20AI.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHickok's%20Center%20for%20AI%20and%20Digital%20Policy%20wrote%20to%20UK%20the%20prime%20minister%2C%20Rishi%20Sunak%2C%20earlier%20in%20the%20month%20to%20urge%20him%20to%20include%20pressing%20issues%20of%20%26quot%3Bbias%2C%20equity%2C%20fairness%2C%20and%20accountability%26quot%3B%20in%20the%20meeting%20agenda.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHickok%20added%20that%20the%20event's%20narrow%20focus%20risked%20sidelining%20these%20other%20threats%20to%20civil%20society.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20UK%20should%20not%20let%20the%20AI%20safety%20agenda%20displace%20the%20AI%20fairness%20agenda%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fuk-ai-summit-ignoring-the-real-threats-posed-by-ai-2023-10%5C%22%3