he%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%20spoke%20to%20some%20of%20those%20who%20have%20alleged%20that%20they%20have%20been%20sexually%20harassed%20by%20teachers%20and%20then%20that%20their%20complaints%20were%20ignored%2C%20not%20acted%20upon%20or%20inadequately%20addressed.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ESeveral%20complaints%20in%20the%20last%20two%20academic%20years%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CMy%20PhD%20advisor%20attempted%20to%20forcibly%20kiss%20me%20and%20engaged%20in%20inappropriate%20touching.%20The%20University%20is%20permitting%20him%20to%20continue%20teaching%2C%20even%20after%20the%20Internal%20Complaints%20Committee%20found%20him%20guilty%20of%20sexual%20harassment.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CHe%20took%20me%20to%20a%20road%20behind%20the%20Natyaghar%2C%20which%20was%20deserted%20and%20there%20all%20of%20sudden%20he%20broke%20down%20in%20tears%20and%20embraced%20me%20tightly%20even%20before%20I%20could%20react.%20He%20quickly%20started%20running%20his%20hands%20all%20over%20my%20body%20and%20started%20rubbing%20his%20against%20mine%20in%20the%20most%20gross%20manner%20that%20one%20can%20imagine.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CMy%20guide%20told%20me%20that%20he%20would%20only%20allow%20me%20to%20submit%20my%20thesis%20if%20I%20met%20him%20alone%20in%20a%20hotel%20room.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThese%20are%20some%20excerpts%20from%20formal%20complaints%20filed%20and%20statements%20made%20by%20students%20at%20Visva-Bharati%20University%20this%20year%20and%20the%20last.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EVisva-Bharati%20was%20founded%20by%20Rabindranath%20Tagore%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fculture%2Fvisva-bharati-university-unesco-living-heritage-art-craft%5C%22%3Ewas%20recently%20declared%20the%20world%E2%80%99s%20first%20living%20heritage%20university%3C%2Fa%3E.%20For%20suffering%20students%20though%2C%20the%20central%20university%20has%20become%20more%20of%20a%20living%20nightmare%20than%20a%20sanctuary%20of%20learning%20and%20peace.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EA%20PhD%20student%20who%20lodged%20a%20complaint%20against%20a%20senior%20teacher%20in%20the%20department%20of%20education%2C%20Rajarshi%20Roy%2C%20said%20that%20Roy%E2%80%99s%20ties%20to%20senior%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%20leaders%20has%20ensured%20for%20him%20a%20degree%20of%20safety%20in%20his%20position.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CRajarshi%20Roy%20is%20my%20PhD%20guide%20and%20a%20powerful%20man.%20He%20is%20related%20to%20an%20influential%20BJP%20MP%20in%20the%20state.%20His%20wife%20is%20a%20BJP%20worker.%20That%E2%80%99s%20why%20he%20remains%20in%20his%20teaching%20position%2C%20despite%20spending%20days%20in%20jail%20over%20rape%20attempt%20charges.%20Because%20of%20his%20political%20influence%2C%20the%20V-C%20is%20protecting%20him%20instead%20of%20following%20the%20ICC%20recommendations%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20PhD%20student%20said.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ERoy%20allegedly%20turned%20down%20the%20student%E2%80%99s%20requests%20for%20pre-PhD%20submission%2C%20extension%2C%20and%20re-registration%2C%20reportedly%20due%20to%20the%20student%E2%80%99s%20refusal%20to%20accept%20his%20alleged%20advances.%20The%20situation%20intensified%20when%20the%20student%20filed%20a%20formal%20complaint%20with%20the%20university%E2%80%99s%20ICC%20in%20June%202022.%20Roy%20pushed%20for%20the%20withdrawal%20of%20the%20complaint%2C%20and%20was%20allegedly%20backed%20by%20another%20faculty%20member%2C%20the%20student%20said.%20With%20no%20response%20from%20the%20authorities%2C%20the%20student%20went%20to%20the%20police%20and%20an%20FIR%20was%20lodged%20against%20the%20guide%20in%20May%2C%2011%20months%20after%20her%20initial%20complaint%20to%20the%20ICC.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Cem%3E%20The%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%20has%20seen%20her%20police%20complaint%2C%20which%20was%20turned%20into%20an%20FIR%2C%20and%20the%20ICC%20complaint%20she%20filed.%20Multiple%20emails%20she%20sent%20Roy%2C%20requesting%20him%20to%20check%20her%20PhD%20work%2C%20were%20also%20seen.%20This%20student%2C%20like%20others%2C%20requested%20anonymity%20for%20this%20piece.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOnly%2048%20minutes%20after%20she%20filed%20the%20police%20complaint%2C%20Sakuntala%20Misra%2C%20the%20chairperson%20of%20the%20ICC%2C%20sent%20out%20the%20report%20that%20had%20actually%20found%20Rajarshi%20Roy%20guilty%20three%20months%20prior%2C%20back%20in%20February%202023.%20Roy%20was%20notably%20implicated%20twice%20in%202016%20and%202019%2C%20in%20cases%20that%20had%20to%20do%20with%20sexual%20harassment.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20ICC%20report%20concluded%3A%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%20%E2%80%9CIt%20is%20established%20and%20confirmed%20that%20the%20respondent%20(Rajarshi%20Roy)%20is%20found%20guilty%20of%20repeated%20offence%20of%20sexual%20harassment%20of%20lady%20as%20per%20provisions%20of%20Section%202(n)%20(i)%2C%20(ii)%2C%20(iii)%20%26amp%3B%20(v)%20of%20the%20Sexual%20Harassment%20of%20Women%20at%20Workplace%20(Prevention%2C%20Prohibition%20and%20Redressal)%20Act%2C%202013%20and%20clause%20D%20(1)%20(i)%2C%20(ii)%2C%20(iii)%20%26amp%3B%20(v)%20of%20the%20Policy%20on%20Prevention%20of%20Sexual%20Harassment%20of%20Women%20at%20Workplace%20(PSHWW)%20of%20Visva-Bharati.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ERajarshi%20Roy%20was%20arrested%20and%20later%20released%20on%20bail.%20Subsequently%2C%20he%20faced%20a%20month-long%20suspension%20from%20the%20University%2C%20but%20has%20since%20returned%20to%20work.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ERoy%E2%80%99s%20phone%20is%20switched%20off%20and%20%3Cem%3EThe%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3Cem%3EWire%3C%2Fem%3E%20has%20not%20been%20able%20to%20reach%20him%20otherwise.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20have%20submitted%20our%20report%20to%20the%20university%20authorities.%20We%20don%E2%80%99t%20have%20anything%20more%20to%20say%2C%E2%80%9D%20Sakuntala%20Misra%20told%20%3Cem%3EThe%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3Cem%3EWire%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAnother%20faculty%20member%2C%20assistant%20professor%20of%20dance%2C%20Sumit%20Basu%2C%20who%20was%20detained%20for%20around%20two%20weeks%20in%20April%202022%20for%20allegedly%20hurling%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hindustantimes.com%2Fcities%2Fkolkata-news%2Fvisva-bharati-asst-professor-arrested-for-alleged-casteist-slur-against-student-101649685687854.html%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Ecastiest%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20abuses%20at%20a%20Dalit%20student.%20However%2C%20Visva-Bharati%20chose%20to%20enforce%20only%20a%20weeklong%20suspension%2C%20which%20went%20against%20the%20established%20rules%20and%20guidelines.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EPrashanta%20Ghosh%2C%20a%20faculty%20member%20in%20the%20department%20of%20music%20at%20Sangeet%20Bhavan%2C%20did%20not%20experience%20any%20repercussions%20despite%20facing%20allegations%20of%20sexual%20harassment%20in%202023.In%20July%202023%2C%20the%20student%20filed%20a%20police%20complaint%2C%20accusing%20Ghosh%20of%20attempted%20molestation.%20In%20the%20police%20complaint%2C%20turned%20into%20an%20FIR%2C%20submitted%20by%20another%20research%20scholar%2C%20it%20she%20reported%20that%20Ghosh%20had%20allegedly%20harassed%20and%20stalked%20her%20over%20an%20extended%20period%2C%20even%20sharing%20pornography%20with%20her%20against%20her%20consent.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%20has%20obtained%20a%20copy%20of%20the%20FIR%20where%20she%20stated%20that%20the%20teacher%20threatened%20to%20ruin%20her%20career%20if%20she%20did%20not%20comply%20with%20his%20requests%3A%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CHe%20made%20it%20clear%20in%20no%20uncertain%20terms%20that%20I%20need%20to%20maintain%20a%20physical%20relationship%20with%20him%20and%20while%20maintaining%20such%20relationship%20I%20should%20mimic%20the%20actions%20of%20the%20actress%2C%20as%20depicted%20in%20the%20said%20pornographic%20clip.%20He%20kept%20a%20vice-like%20grip%20on%20me%20by%20misusing%20his%20position%20of%20authority%20over%20me%20and%20repeatedly%20threatened%20to%20ruin%20my%20career%20including%20threats%20to%20make%20my%20exam%20papers%20disappear.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EProfessor%20Arnab%20Ghosh%20from%20the%20Department%20of%20Anthropology%20also%20faces%20several%20allegations%20of%20sexual%20harassment%20since%202021%2C%20as%20well%20as%20charges%20of%20caste%20and%20gender%20discrimination.%20One%20research%20scholar%20has%20said%20that%20she%20was%20refused%20maternity%20leave%2C%20while%20another%20has%20alleged%20she%20was%20called%20a%20%E2%80%9Cbeggar%E2%80%9D%20for%20requesting%20a%20fellowship%20grant.%20Several%20students%20also%20reported%20instances%20where%20Ghosh%20allegedly%20tied%20the%20progress%20of%20their%20theses%20to%20their%20willingness%20to%20%E2%80%9Cmeet%20him%20in%20a%20hotel.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CHe%20rejected%20my%20promotion%20from%20Junior%20Research%20Fellow%20to%20Senior%20Research%20Fellow%20despite%20my%20post-graduation%20with%20distinction%20from%20one%20of%20India%E2%80%99s%20most%20prestigious%20research%20institutes.%20On%20multiple%20occasions%2C%20he%20lewdly%20told%20me%20to%20%E2%80%98go%20and%20have%20fun%E2%80%99%20with%20my%20husband%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20one%20of%20the%20complainants%20who%20adds%20that%20she%20lost%20a%20fellowship%20grant%20of%20nearly%20Rs%2012%20lakh%20as%20a%20result.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EA%20member%20of%20Ghosh%E2%80%99s%20family%20told%20%3Cem%3EThe%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3Cem%3EWire%3C%2Fem%3E%20that%20Ghosh%20would%20contact%20this%20writer.%20This%20report%20will%20be%20updated%20when%20he%20does.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOn%20August%2011%20and%2012%2C%20two%20posts%20surfaced%20on%20a%20Facebook%20group%20called%20%E2%80%98VB%20Confessions%E2%80%99.%20Such%20%E2%80%98confessions%E2%80%99%20pages%20are%20common%20for%20educational%20institutions%20and%20offer%20students%20anonymity%20when%20they%20write%20it.%20In%20the%20posts%2C%20students%20asserted%20that%20they%20were%20%E2%80%9Cphysically%20and%20mentally%20tortured%20by%20multiple%20teachers%E2%80%9D%20in%20the%20music%20department.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3EInstead%20of%20investigating%20these%20claims%2C%20the%20university%20dismissed%20the%20allegations%20outright%2C%20labelling%20them%20as%20a%20malicious%20campaign%20against%20an%20internationally%20reputed%20institution.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EV%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3Eice-Chancellor%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hindustantimes.com%2Fcities%2Fkolkata-news%2Fvisva-bharati-university-social-media-post-alleges-student-sexually-harassed-101692109847401.html%5C%22%3EBidyut%20Chakrabarty%20staged%20a%20nine-hour%20hunger%20strike%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20campus%20in%20protest%20against%20these%20posts.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ELetters%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20students%20have%20made%20multiple%20attempts%20to%20have%20their%20concerns%20addressed.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20addition%20to%20the%20ICC%2C%20they%20have%20sent%20several%20letters%20to%20the%20PMO%2C%20the%20President%20of%20India%2C%20the%20National%20Commission%20for%20Women%2C%20the%20Human%20Rights%20Commission%2C%20the%20National%20Commission%20for%20OBC%2C%20the%20University%20Grants%20Commission%2C%20the%20Ministry%20of%20Education%2C%20and%20the%20Ministry%20of%20Women%20and%20Child%20Development.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F02141049%2FWhatsApp-Image-2023-11-02-at-11.09.41-AM.jpeg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F02141049%2FWhatsApp-Image-2023-11-02-at-11.09.41-AM.jpeg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F02141049%2FWhatsApp-Image-2023-11-02-at-11.09.41-AM-300x133.jpeg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F02141049%2FWhatsApp-Image-2023-11-02-at-11.09.41-AM-1024x452.jpeg%201024w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-683143%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22530%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EOne%20of%20the%20emails%20sent%20by%20students%20to%20the%20PMO.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EDespite%20these%20appeals%2C%20the%20Vice-Chancellor%2C%20known%20for%20frequently%20making%20controversial%20statements%2C%20has%20not%20taken%20significant%20action%20to%20address%20these%20grave%20allegations.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Cem%3EThe%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3Cem%3EWire%3C%2Fem%3E%20reached%20out%20to%20the%20University%20and%20Mahua%20Banerjee%2C%20in%20charge%20of%20public%20relations%20there%2C%20stated%2C%20%E2%80%9CWe%20will%20decide%20as%20per%20due%20processes%20applicable%20to%20all%20who%20are%20associated%20with%20the%20university.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EProfessor%20Sudipta%20Bhattacharya%2C%20president%20of%20the%20Visva-Bharati%20University%20Faculty%20Association%20and%20a%20faculty%20member%20in%20the%20department%20of%20economics%20and%20politics%20at%20Vidya%20Bhavana%20said%20that%20he%20was%20recently%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Feducation%2Fpolitical-vendetta-alleged-in-suspension-of-visva-bharati-professor%5C%22%3Eserved%20with%20a%20chargesheet%20for%20filing%20an%20FIR%3C%2Fa%3E%20against%20the%20VC%20for%20an%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%