0students.%20Most%20of%20interim%20court%20orders%20have%20been%20against%20the%20university.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EAparna%20Bhattacharya%20is%20a%20Kolkata-based%20political%20analyst%20with%20experience%20in%20campaign%20strategy%2C%20communication%20and%20public%20affairs.%20She%20is%20co-founder%20of%20Populytix%2C%20a%20data%20analysis%20and%20market%20research%20firm.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1698914147000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F19180125%2Fimage-1-1.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fvisva-bharati-university-sexual-harassment%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20university%20has%20seen%20numerous%20show-cause%20notices%20and%20suspension%20orders%20issued%20to%20students%20and%20teachers%20since%20controversial%20V-C%20Bidyut%20Chakrabarty%20assumed%20his%20position%20in%20November%202018.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A1%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fvisva-bharati-university-sexual-harassment%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Apple%20may%20look%20at%20India%20for%20development%20of%20new%20iPhone%20model%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1698914142000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-104911099%2Cimgsize-524130.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fgadgets-news%2Fapple-may-look-at-india-for-development-of-new-iphone-model-for-the-first-time-outside-china%2Farticleshow%2F104911099.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Apple%20may%20start%20developing%20a%20new%20iPhone%20model%20outside%20of%20China%20for%20the%20first%20time%2C%20with%20the%20iPhone%2017%20potentially%20being%20developed%20in%20India%2C%20according%20to%20Apple%20analyst%20Ming-Chi%20Kuo.%20This%20move%20is%20part%20of%20Apple's%20broader%20strategy%20to%20diversify%20its%20supply%20chain%20away%20from%20China.%20Last%20w