rthquake%20strikes%20central%20Philippines%3A%20USGS%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1698911009000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-104910327%2Cimgsize-59130.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Frest-of-world%2Fmagnitude-5-7-earthquake-strikes-central-philippines-usgs%2Farticleshow%2F104910291.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F104910291.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3EAn%20earthquake%20of%20magnitude%205.7%20struck%20the%20central%20Philippines%20on%20Tuesday%2C%20the%20USGS%20said.%20The%20offshore%20quake%20was%20at%20a%20depth%20of%2019.2%20km%20(12%20miles)%2C%20USGS%20said%2C%20off%20the%20central%20province%20of%20Eastern%20Samar.%20The%20Philippine%20Institute%20of%20Volcanology%20and%20Seismology%20warned%20of%20damage%20and%20aftershocks%20in%20an%20advisory%20but%20there%20were%20no%20immediate%20reports%20of%20casualties.%20The%20Philippines%20lies%20on%20the%20%26quot%3BRing%20of%20Fire%26quot%3B%2C%20a%20belt%20of%20volcanoes%20circling%20the%20Pacific%20Ocean%20that%20is%20prone%20to%20earthquakes.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Frest-of-world%2Fmagnitude-5-7-earthquake-strikes-central-philippines-usgs%2Farticleshow%2F104910291.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fm-timesofindia-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fm.timesofindia.com%2Fworld%2Frest-of-world%2Fmagnitude-5-7-earthquake-strikes-central-philippines-usgs%2Famp_articleshow%2F104910291.cms%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fm.timesofindia.com%2Fworld%2Frest-of-world%2Fmagnitude-5-7-earthquake-strikes-central-philippines-usgs%2Famp_articleshow%2F104910291.cms%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Bihar%20Caste%20Survey%3A%20The%20Who%E2%80%99s%20Who%20in%20the%20Data%20%7C%20Madaria%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F02123121%2FBihar-Kosi-River-Story-Photo-Manoj-Singh-text.jpeg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EBeyond%20politics%2C%20the%20Bihar%20caste%20survey%20is%20a%20revolutionary%20document.%C2%A0%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EA%20public%20document%2C%20the%20first%20ever%20after%201931%2C%20allowing%20for%20people%20to%20stand%20up%20and%20be%20counted.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EWe%20go%20down%20to%20the%20wire%2C%20on%20what%20each%20of%20the%20numbers%20unveiled%20mean.%C2%A0%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EWho%20are%20the%20people%20referred%20to%20by%20percentages%20in%20the%20survey%3F%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EToday%20we%20look%20at%20Madaria.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%C2%A7%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ECastes%20were%20not%20created%20in%20the%20heavens.%20Nor%20did%20God%20ask%20humans%20to%20discriminate%20amongst%20themselves.%20There%20is%20no%20dearth%20of%20evidence%20for%20this.%20One%20such%20piece%20of%20evidence%20is%20existence%20of%20the%20Madaria%20people%20%E2%80%93%20a%20caste%20which%20came%20into%20being%20during%20the%20British%20rule%2C%20after%201857.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThis%20isolated%20caste%20is%20present%20only%20in%20the%20border%20districts%20of%20Bihar%20and%20Jharkhand.%20No%20matter%20how%20hard%20you%20try%2C%20you%20will%20not%20be%20able%20to%20locate%20members%20of%20this%20caste%20anywhere%20else.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ETheir%20story%20is%20not%20very%20old%20but%20it%20has%20not%20been%20recorded%20in%20history%20in%20a%20systematic%20manner.%20Ethnographers%20never%20paid%20attention%20to%20them.%20Most%20sociologists%20also%20did%20not%20give%20them%20much%20importance.%20Madarias%20currently%20live%20in%20Sanhaula%20and%20Dhoraiya%20blocks%20of%20two%20districts%20of%20Bihar%20%E2%80%93%20Bhagalpur%20and%20Banka%20respectively.%20But%20who%20are%20they%20and%20what%20earned%20them%20the%20name%20Madaria%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20337px)%2085vw%2C%20337px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F30093107%2FIMG_2742.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22337%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F30093107%2FIMG_2742.jpg%20838w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F30093107%2FIMG_2742-210x300.jpg%20210w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F30093107%2FIMG_2742-715x1024.jpg%20715w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-682410%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22483%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EIllustration%3A%20Pariplab%20Chakraborty%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cp%3ELet%20us%20first%20find%20out%20about%20their%20traditional%20profession.%20The%20members%20of%20the%20Madaria%20caste%20have%20largely%20been%20engaged%20in%20farming.%20Most%20of%20them%20own%20tiny%20tracts%20of%20land%20where%20they%20grow%20food%20to%20sustain%20them%20for%20three%20to%20six%20months.%20For%20the%20rest%20of%20the%20year%2C%20they%20have%20to%20work%20as%20agricultural%20or%20daily%20wage%20labourers%2C%20building%20and%20painting%20houses%2C%20working%20in%20grocery%20shops%20or%20sorting%20grain%20in%20the%20markets.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAt%20this%20point%20one%20might%20be%20wondering%20whether%20they%20are%20Hindu%20or%20Muslim.%20If%20they%20are%20Hindus%2C%20one%20might%20further%20wonder%20if%20they%20are%20a%20so-called%20%E2%80%98untouchable%E2%80%99%20caste.%20I%20would%20not%20be%20surprised%20if%20such%20questions%20come%20to%20your%20mind.%20As%20stated%20above%2C%20castes%20were%20not%20created%20in%20heavens%2C%20and%20it%20was%20on%20the%20earth%20that%20inhabitants%20created%20religions%20and%20castes%20to%20identify%20themselves.%20For%20example%2C%20someone%20who%20rears%20cows%20and%20buffaloes%20is%20a%20Gwala%20or%20Yadav.%20Someone%20who%20makes%20comfortable%20shoes%20and%20other%20items%20from%20leather%20is%20a%20Chamar.%20Someone%20who%20beautifies%20people%20by%20shaving%20hair%20is%20a%20Nayi.%20If%20someone%20makes%20society%20clean%20by%20washing%20the%20dirty%20clothes%20of%20others%2C%20he%20is%20a%20Dhobi%2C%20and%20if%20someone%20cultivates%20paddy%2C%20he%20is%20a%20Dhanuk.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20people%20of%20the%20Madaria%20caste%20are%20basically%20Dhanuks%2C%20and%20categorised%20as%20Madaria%20Muslims%20and%20Dhanuk%20Hindus.%20The%20Dhanuks%20of%20Bihar%20are%20no%20longer%20the%20same%20Dhanuks%20who%20used%20to%20add%20the%20word%20Mandal%20to%20their%20names.%20Now%2C%20they%20consider%20themselves%20equivalent%20to%20the%20Kurmi%20caste%20living%20in%20the%20area%20south%20of%20the%20Ganges.%20It%20is%20a%20matter%20of%20research%20why%20the%20Kurmis%20living%20in%20the%20districts%20like%20Patna%2C%20Nalanda%2C%20Jehanabad%2C%20Gaya%2C%20Nawada%2C%20etc.%20have%20huge%20land%20holdings%2C%20whereas%20in%20the%20region%20where%20the%20Ganga%20crosses%20the%20state%20boundary%2C%20the%20Dhanuks%20have%20smaller%20land%20holdings.%20Could%20there%20be%20a%20connection%20or%20is%20it%20political%20propaganda%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20population%20of%20Dhanuks%2C%20according%20to%20the%20report%20of%20the%20caste-based%20survey%20conducted%20by%20the%20Bihar%20government%2C%20is%202%2C796%2C605.%20One%20can%20observe%20that%20the%20caste%20is%20widely%20spread%20in%20areas%20of%20North%20Bihar.%20Meanwhile%2C%20the%20total%20population%20of%20Kurmis%20in%20the%20state%20as%20per%20the%20report%20of%20the%20Bihar%20government%20is%203%2C762%2C969.%20If%20one%20adds%20the%20population%20of%20the%20Madaria%20caste%20to%20it%2C%20that%20is%2C%2086%2C665%2C%20the%20total%20is%206%2C646%2C239.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EBefore%20analysing%20the%20political%20implications%20of%20the%20data%2C%20one%20may%20ask%20why%20the%20people%20of%20Madaria%20caste%20accepted%20Islam.%20Was%20there%20any%20pressure%20on%20them%3F%20Had%20any%20Muslim%20ruler%20persecuted%20them%20and%20forced%20them%20to%20do%20so%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAs%20already%20mentioned%2C%20this%20caste%20came%20into%20existence%20during%20the%20British%20era%20post%201857.%20At%20that%20time%2C%20there%20was%20no%20fear%20of%20any%20Muslim%20ruler%20in%20the%20region%20of%20Bihar%20inhabited%20by%20the%20people%20of%20this%20caste.%20But%20there%20was%20certainly%20the%20influence%20of%20saints%20or%20%3Cem%3Epeer%3C%2Fem%3E%E2%80%93%3Cem%3Efakirs%3C%2Fem%3E.%20The%20impact%20was%20such%20that%20Bhagalpur%2C%20an%20industrial%20city%20situated%20on%20the%20banks%20of%20Ganga%2C%20which%20was%20once%20famous%20for%20silk%20clothes%2C%20is%20named%20after%20a%20Peer%20%E2%80%93%20Bhagalu%20Mian%20%E2%80%93%20whose%20tomb%20stands%20in%20the%20centre%20of%20the%20city%20even%20today.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ETherefore%2C%20it%20is%20clear%20that%20when%20the%20Madaria%20people%20accepted%20Islam%2C%20they%20did%20it%20out%20of%20their%20own%20will%20and%20awareness.%20It%20is%20possible%20that%20they%20had%20learned%20from%20the%20saints%20that%20there%20is%20no%20caste%20discrimination%20in%20Islam%2C%20unlike%20Hinduism.%20No%20matter%20which%20caste%20a%20person%20belongs%20to%2C%20no%20one%20discriminates%20against%20anyone.%20In%20the%20mosque%2C%20everyone%20prays%20together%20and%20embraces%20each%20other.%20After%20embracing%20Islam%20one%20also%20does%20not%20have%20to%20take%20a%20dip%20in%20the%20Ganga.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThis%20is%20what%20might%20have%20happened%20with%20the%20Madaria%20people.%20They%20accepted%20Islam%20but%20their%20caste%20stayed%20with%20them%20for%20a%20long%20time.%20This%20is%20why%20they%20kept%20using%20the%20surname%20%E2%80%93%20Mandal.%20Even%20today%2C%20names%20like%20Suleman%20Mandal%2C%20Rahim%20Mandal%20or%20Ashfaq%20Mandal%C2%A0can%20be%20seen%20in%20land%20deeds.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ELater%2C%20their%20understanding%20of%20Islam%20expanded%20and%20they%20shed%20their%20Hindu%20identity.%20But%20then%20they%20were%20faced%20with%20the%20dilemma%20of%20the%20names%20to%20use.%20They%20could%20neither%20identify%20themselves%20with%20Syed%2C%20Shaikh%20or%20Pathan%20on%20the%20pattern%20of%20Hindu%20upper%20castes%20nor%20were%20they%20like%20the%20Qureshis%20or%20the%20Lalbegis%20or%20Halalkhors.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ELater%2C%20they%20would%20have%20opted%20for%20a%20different%20set%20of%20surnames%20for%20themselves.%20If%20they%20faced%20opposition%2C%20the%20next%20generation%20would%20have%20switched%20to%20other%20names.%20Again%2C%20it%20is%20because%20castes%20were%20not%20created%20in%20heavens%20but%20are%20man-made.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20situation%20changed%20when%20the%20country%20gained%20independence%20and%20the%20question%20of%20reservation%20arose.%20The%20people%20of%20the%20Madaria%20community%20accepted%20that%20they%20are%20neither%20Dhanuks%20nor%20Ashraf%20Muslims.%20They%20are%20either%20landless%20or%20farmers%20with%20very%20small%20land%20holdings%2C%20whose%20social%20status%20is%20in%20accordance%20with%20this.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20fact%2C%20social%20status%20in%20this%20country%20is%20proportional%20to%20the%20rights%20on%20land.%20That%20is%2C%20the%20more%20land%20one%20has%2C%20the%20higher%20one%E2%80%99s%20status.%20If%20the%20Madaria%20people%20have%20smaller%20land%20holdings%2C%20their%20status%20is%20also%20low.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EWell%20before%20the%20implementation%20of%20the%20Mandal%20Commission%20recommendations%2C%20when%20the%20recommendations%20of%20the%20Mungerilal%20Commission%20were%20implemented%20in%20Bihar%20in%201978%2C%20Madaria%20people%20were%20also%20declared%20entitled%20to%20reservation%20and%20they%20were%20placed%20in%20the%20category%20of%20Yadavs%2C%20Kurmi%2C%20Kushwaha-Koeri%20etc.%20This%20continued%20until%20Nitish%20Kumar%20came%20to%20power%20and%20the%20caste%20was%20declared%20an%20extremely%20backward%20class.%20This%20had%20political%20implications%20as%20the%20decision%20was%20taken%20to%20cause%20a%20dent%20in%20the%20support%20base%20of%20Lalu%20Prasad%20Yadav.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EBut%20beyond%20politics%2C%20Madarias%20are%20still%20present%20in%20the%20paddy%20fields%20of%20this%20region.%20Now%2C%20the%20people%20of%20this%20caste%20have%20adopted%20other%20professions%20because%20farming%20is%20no%20longer%20as%20profitable.%20In%20addition%2C%20their%20population%20has%20increased%20but%20the%20size%20of%20land%20holdings%20is%20just%20as%20small.%20After%20the%20separation%20of%20Jharkhand%2C%20the%20situation%20became%20even%20more%20difficult.%20Earlier%20the%20caste%20had%20a%20sizeable%20population%2C%20due%20to%20which%20they%20played%20an%20important%20role%20in%20elections.%20They%20are%20still%20quite%20a%20significant%20vote%20bank%20at%20least%20in%20Sanhaula%20of%20Bhagalpur%20and%20Dhoraiya%20of%20Banka%2C%20where%20they%20hold%20an%20influence%20on%20the%20poll%20outcome.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3ETranslated%20from%20Hindi%20by%20Naushin%20Rehman.%20Read%20the%20Hindi%20original%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewirehindi.com%2F260204%2Fbihar-caste-survey-how-madariyas-originated%2F%5C%22%3Ehere%3C%2Fa%3E.%3Cbr%3E%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3ERead%20part%20one%20of%20the%20series%2C%20on%20the%20Ghasi%20community%2C%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcaste%2Fbihar-caste-survey-the-whos-who-in-the-data-ghasi%5C%22%3Ehere%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%20part%20two%20on%20the%20Santrash%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcaste%2Fbihar-caste-survey-the-whos-who-in-the-data-santrash%5C%22%3Ehere%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThe%20series%20is%20available%20in%20Hindi%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewirehindi.com%2F260200%2Fbihar-caste-survey-who-are-the-santarash%2F%5C%22%3Ehere%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0and%20in%20Urdu%2C%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewireurdu.com%2Fauthor%2Fnaval-kishor-kumar%2F%5C%22%3Eher