ith%20almost%20no%20real%20information%20about%20what%E2%80%99s%20being%20done%2C%20if%20anything%2C%20about%20saving%20their%20lives%20and%20securing%20their%20freedom%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3ETaking%20the%20game%20%E2%80%98deep%E2%80%99%2C%20a%20big%20mistake%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20cricket%20terms%2C%20it%E2%80%99s%20the%20risky%20approach%20of%20taking%20the%20game%20%E2%80%98deep%E2%80%99%20during%20a%20tough%20run-chase.%20Instead%20of%20pushing%20for%20the%20occasional%20boundary%20in%20the%20middle%20overs%2C%20the%20batters%20go%20into%20a%20defensive%2C%20%E2%80%98doing-very-little%E2%80%99%20mode%2C%20hoping%20to%20catch%20up%20in%20the%20death%20overs.%20Except%20by%20then%2C%20the%20required%20run%20rate%20gets%20too%20high%2C%20and%20the%20game%20is%20lost.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EDid%20India%20hold%20off%20pushing%20hard%2C%20and%20at%20the%20required%20top-most%20level%2C%20for%20the%20freedom%20of%20the%20%E2%80%98Qatar%208%E2%80%99%3F%20And%20has%20that%20now%20made%20an%20already%20tough%20task%2C%20exponentially%20harder%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThere%20are%20three%20questions%20to%20answer%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EFirst%2C%20did%20India%20underestimate%20Qatar%3F%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3ESecond%2C%20how%20does%20the%20%E2%80%98death%20sentence%E2%80%99%20impact%20India%E2%80%99s%20position%3F%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThird%2C%20does%20the%20Gaza%20conflict%20further%20complicate%20this%20matter%3F%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EQatar%20raised%20the%20stakes%20in%202022%20itself%2C%20which%20India%20missed%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ELet%E2%80%99s%20also%20understand%20that%20the%20exact%20nature%20of%20the%20charges%20against%20the%20Qatar%208%20has%20now%20receded%20in%20relevance.%20People%20in%20India%20may%20have%20pointed%20out%20months%20ago%20that%20none%20of%20these%20men%20had%20dealt%20with%20submarines%20in%20their%20naval%20careers%2C%20and%20yet%20were%20reportedly%20charged%20with%20%E2%80%98spying%20on%20behalf%20of%20Israel%E2%80%99%20for%20information%20about%20%E2%80%98stealth%20technology%E2%80%99%20in%20Italian%20midget%20submarines.%20We%20may%20have%20also%20asked%20why%20Israel%20would%20need%20details%20of%20Italian%20submarine%20tech%2C%20when%20it%20has%20unfettered%20access%20to%20all%20this%2C%20and%20more%2C%20from%20the%20US.%20But%20the%20time%20for%20raising%20such%20questions%20has%20passed.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EMore%20worryingly%2C%20it%20seems%20the%20Indian%20government%20may%20not%20have%20realised%20how%20high%20Qatar%20had%20raised%20the%20stakes%20in%20this%20case%2C%20at%20the%20very%20outset.%20Considering%20that%20the%20eight%20men%20were%20picked%20up%20in%20the%20dead%20of%20night%2C%20with%20their%20own%20families%20not%20being%20given%20any%20details%20for%20weeks%2C%20with%20India%E2%80%99s%20embassy%20in%20Qatar%20having%20no%20initial%20idea%20about%20their%20whereabouts%2C%20let%20alone%20getting%20consular%20and%20legal%20access%20%E2%80%93%20it%20should%20have%20been%20clear%20back%20then%20that%20the%20charges%2C%20whatever%20they%20may%20be%2C%20were%20being%20taken%20very%20seriously%20by%20Qatar.%20And%20that%20Qatar%20itself%2C%20needed%20to%20be%20taken%20more%20seriously.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EUnderestimating%20Doha%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EQatar%20has%20grown%20in%20stature%20as%20a%20pivotal%20state%20in%20West%20Asia.%20It%20hosted%20the%20crucial%20US-Taliban%20talks%20%E2%80%93%20that%20alone%20underlines%20how%20smartly%20it%20has%20positioned%20itself%2C%20acceptable%20to%20polar%20opposites%20as%20a%20%E2%80%98neutral%E2%80%99%20venue%20for%20talks.%20Even%20as%20Qatar%20plays%20host%20to%20a%20crucial%20US%20air%20base%2C%20it%20also%20permits%20Hamas%20to%20run%20a%20full-fledged%20office%20on%20its%20soil.%20Doha%20is%20also%20the%20headquarters%20of%20the%20Al%20Jazeera%20media%20network%2C%20which%20presents%20a%20powerful%20counter-narrative%20to%20events%20in%20the%20region%20in%20contrast%20to%20most%20Western%20media%20reportage.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20bilateral%20terms%20too%2C%20Doha%20has%20been%20on%20the%20ascendant%2C%20subtly%20demanding%20more%20respect%20from%20India.%20On%20the%20economic%20front%2C%20Qatar%20supplies%20India%20with%2040%25%20of%20its%20liquified%20natural%20gas%20(LNG)%20fuel.%20Qatar%E2%80%99s%20exports%20to%20India%20are%20worth%20almost%20%2417%20billion%2C%20way%20more%20than%20India%E2%80%99s%20exports%20to%20Qatar%20(less%20than%20%242%20billion).%20Also%2C%20around%207%20lakh%20Indians%20make%20a%20living%20in%20Qatar%2C%20remitting%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fpib.gov.in%2FPressReleasePage.aspx%3FPRID%3D1897036%5C%22%3Ecrores%20of%20rupees%3C%2Fa%3E%20back%20home%20and%20into%20India%E2%80%99s%20economy.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F02122503%2F50588963473_ebdfad581b_k.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F02122503%2F50588963473_ebdfad581b_k.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F02122503%2F50588963473_ebdfad581b_k-300x200.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F02122503%2F50588963473_ebdfad581b_k-1024x683.jpg%201024w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-683108%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22800%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3ERepresentative%20image%20of%20migrant%20workers%20in%20Qatar.%20Photo%3A%20ILO%2FFlickr%20CC%20BY%20NC%20ND%202.0%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EPaying%20the%20price%20of%20%E2%80%98hate%E2%80%99%20at%20home%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EBut%20beyond%20the%20economy%2C%20Qatar%2C%20more%20than%20most%20other%20Arab%20nations%20in%20recent%20times%2C%20has%20been%20vocal%20about%20the%20steep%20rise%20in%20anti-Muslim%20rhetoric%20and%20violence%20in%20India.%20When%20BJP%20spokesperson%20Nupur%20Sharma%20made%20derogatory%20remarks%20about%20Prophet%20Mohammed%2C%20Qatar%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fdiplomacy%2Fqatar-summons-indian-envoy-seeks-govts-public-apology-over-bjp-leaders-remarks-on-prophet%5C%22%3Eled%20the%20chorus%20of%20Arab%20condemnation%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Sharma%E2%80%99s%20token%20apology%20and%20equally%20token%20suspension%20from%20the%20BJP%20is%20not%20likely%20to%20have%20impressed%20Qatar%2C%20as%20the%20radical%20Hindutva%20violence%20and%20hate%20have%20only%20gathered%20more%20momentum%20in%20India.%20Most%20recently%2C%20all%20was%20forgiven%20in%20the%20case%20of%20serial%20hate%20offender%2C%20Telangana%20MLA%20Raja%20Singh%2C%20as%20his%20suspension%20from%20the%20BJP%20was%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Ftelangana-bjp-suspension-t-raja-singh-comments-prophet-muhammad%5C%22%3Erevoked%3C%2Fa%3E%20ahead%20of%20the%20state%20assembly%20elections.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20BJP%20may%20have%20calculated%20that%20Modi%E2%80%99s%20%E2%80%98personalised%E2%80%99%20reach-outs%20to%20the%20leaders%20of%20the%20Arab%20nations%20in%20recent%20years%20may%20get%20them%20to%20look%20away%20from%20the%20constantly%20rising%20anti-Muslim%20tide%20in%20India.%20But%20has%20that%20happened%3F%20Unfortunately%20not.%20No%20amount%20of%20back-channel%20diplomacy%20has%20been%20able%20to%20soften%20Qatar%E2%80%99s%20attitude%20towards%20the%20eight%20former%20sailors.%20Also%2C%20why%20should%20India%E2%80%99s%20diplomacy%20in%20West%20Asia%20be%20constantly%20undermined%20and%20come%20undone%20by%20the%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20domestic%20majoritarian%20politics%3F%20And%20why%20should%20these%20eight%20Indian%20citizens%2C%20with%20death%20sentences%20hanging%20over%20them%2C%20pay%20the%20price%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20Read%20%7C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fcoursemate-appeal-indian-navy-veterans-death-row-qatar%5C%22%3EA%20Coursemate%20Appeals%3A%20Bring%20Back%20Indian%20Navy%20Veterans%20on%20Death%20Row%20in%20Qatar%20Now%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3ECalling%20up%20the%20Emir%3A%20Is%20it%20way%20too%20late%3F%3C%2Fb%3E%3Cb%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20key%20question%20is%3A%20When%20was%20the%20most%20opportune%20time%20for%20India%E2%80%99s%20prime%20minister%20to%20pick%20up%20the%20phone%20and%20ask%20the%20Emir%20of%20Qatar%2C%20Sheikh%20Tamim%20Al%20Thani%2C%20to%20be%20magnanimous%20and%20pardon%20our%20men%3F%20Almost%20anyone%20not%20looking%20at%20this%20through%20the%20lens%20of%20the%202024%20election%2C%20would%20say%20that%20moment%20was%20long%20ago.%20The%20almost%20complete%20denial%20of%20access%20to%20the%20eight%20sailors%2C%20the%20gravity%20of%20the%20charges%2C%20and%20the%20intransigence%20of%20the%20Qatar%20government%20should%20have%20underlined%20the%20urgent%20need%20for%20intervention%20at%20the%20very%20top%20%E2%80%93%20before%20the%20array%20of%20formal%20charges%2C%20before%20a%20formal%20legal%20process%20commenced%2C%20and%20certainly%20long%20before%20the%20death%20sentences%20were%20passed.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ENow%2C%20instead%20of%20asking%20merely%20for%20them%20to%20be%20set%20free%2C%20the%20starting%20point%20of%20any%20new%20round%20of%20diplomacy%20or%20phone%20calls%20will%20be%20about%20cancelling%20the%20death%20sentences.%20After%20a%20pardon%2C%20it%20would%20then%20be%20another%20arduous%20push%20for%20shorter%20prison%20sentences.%20And%20if%20that%20were%20achieved%2C%20it%20would%20be%20another%20long%20haul%20to%20request%20Qatar%20to%20allow%20the%20men%20to%20serve%20their%20terms%20in%20Indian%20prisons.%20And%20after%20that%2C%20it%20would%20be%20an%20almost%20impossible%20task%2C%20for%20India%20to%20get%20all%20charges%20to%20be%20dropped%2C%20and%20for%20the%20men%20to%20walk%20free.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EGaza%20conflict%20hurts%20chances%20of%20a%20%E2%80%98pardon%E2%80%99%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EBut%20that%E2%80%99s%20not%20all.%20Let%E2%80%99s%20now%20add%20to%20this%20list%20of%20challenges%20the%20fact%20that%20we%20are%20in%20the%20middle%20of%20a%20full-blown%2C%20bloody%20conflict%20in%20Gaza.%20Qatar%20is%20an%20extremely%20vocal%20critic%20of%20Israel%2C%20even%20relative%20to%20other%20Arab%20nations.%20In%20such%20a%20situation%20%E2%80%93%20when%20a%20court%20in%20Doha%20has%20pronounced%20the%20%E2%80%98Qatar%208%E2%80%99%20guilty%20of%20espionage%20on%20behalf%20of%20Israel%2C%20and%20issued%20the%20most%20serious%20punishment%20possible%20%E2%80%93%20what%20space%2C%20if%20any%2C%20is%20left%20for%20our%20diplomats%20to%20manoeuvre%3F%20Did%20our%20diplomats%20and%20the%20prime%20minister%20not%20foresee%20this%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAs%20the%20casualties%20mount%20in%20Gaza%2C%20including%20thousands%20of%20civilians%2C%20with%20every%20news%20story%20coming%20through%20of%20hospitals%2C%20refugee%20camps%20and%20homes%20being%20targeted%2C%20with%20every%20visual%20of%20Israel%20employing%20its%20full%20military%20might%20to%20flatten%20Gaza%2C%20starve%20and%20choke%20its%20population%20%E2%80%93%20it%20becomes%20almost%20hard%20to%20imagine%20how%20someone%20found%20guilty%20of%20spying%20for%20Israel%20in%20Qatar%2C%20may%20be%20pardoned.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ESo%20now%2C%20what%20consolation%20can%20we%20genuinely%20offer%20to%20the%20eight%20families%3F%20Can%20we%20confidently%20say%20to%20them%2C%20wait%20for%20a%20Ramadan%20%E2%80%98miracle%E2%80%99%20in%202024%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fauthor%2Frohit-khanna%5C%22%3ERohit%20Khanna%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%20a%20journalist%20and%20video%20storyteller.%20He%20has%20been%20managing%20editor%20of%20%3C%2Fem%3EThe%20Quint%2C%3Cem%3E%20and%20is%20a%20two-time%20Ramnath%20Goenka%20Award%20winner.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E