%20that%20influence%20to%20ensure%20respect%20for%20the%20rules%20of%20war%2C%20deescalate%20the%20conflict%20and%20avoid%20a%20spillover%2C%E2%80%9D%20Griffiths%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ERead%20the%20full%20statement%20below.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%C2%A7%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EScores%20of%20civilians%20have%20reportedly%20been%20killed%20in%20Gaza%20following%20recent%20attacks%20on%20the%20Jabalia%20refugee%20camp.%20This%20is%20just%20the%20latest%20atrocity%20to%20befall%20the%20people%20of%20Gaza%20where%20the%20fighting%20has%20entered%20an%20even%20more%20terrifying%20phase%2C%20with%20increasingly%20dreadful%20humanitarian%20consequences.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EOctober%207th%20and%20its%20aftermath%20will%20leave%20indelible%20scars%20on%20the%20lives%20of%20millions.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20Israel%2C%20a%20nation%20was%20left%20in%20shock%20after%20the%20brutal%20and%20graphic%20killing%20of%20some%201%2C400%20people.%20The%20families%20of%20more%20than%20200%20hostages%20continue%20to%20live%20in%20anguish%2C%20unsure%20about%20the%20fate%2C%20wellbeing%20and%20whereabouts%20of%20their%20loved%20ones.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20Gaza%2C%20women%2C%20children%20and%20men%20are%20being%20starved%2C%20traumatized%20and%20bombed%20to%20death.%20They%20have%20lost%20all%20faith%20in%20humanity%20and%20all%20hope%20of%20a%20future.%20Their%20despair%20is%20palpable.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20West%20Bank%2C%20the%20death%20toll%20is%20rising.%20Violence%20and%20the%20closure%20of%20checkpoints%20mean%20that%20people%20cannot%20access%20food%2C%20jobs%2C%20health%20care%20and%20other%20essential%20services.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20the%20world%20seems%20unable%2C%20or%20unwilling%2C%20to%20act.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThis%20cannot%20go%20on.%20We%20need%20a%20step%20change.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EWe%20need%20the%20hostages%20to%20be%20released%20immediately%20and%20unconditionally.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EWe%20need%20to%20be%20able%20to%20provide%20the%20essentials%20for%20surv