ed%20opacity%20and%20opened%20the%20floodgates%20for%20anonymous%20donations%20to%20parties%2C%20dealing%20a%20severe%20blow%20to%20voters%E2%80%99%20right%20to%20know.%20People%E2%80%99s%20ability%20to%20track%20donations%20by%20big%20businesses%20and%20expose%20%3Cem%3Equid%20pro%20quo%3C%2Fem%3E%20have%20been%20severely%20undermined.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3Ciframe%20allowfullscreen%3D%5C%22allowfullscreen%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fembed%2FY8QqPByG9k8%3Fsi%3DqBA7xsCsZFqUyCnH%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22100%25%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22YouTube%20video%20player%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22504%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%20data-mce-type%3D%5C%22bookmark%5C%22%3E%EF%BB%BF%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cp%3EResponses%20to%20Right%20to%20Information%20(RTI)%20applications%20reveal%20that%20the%20government%20was%20forewarned%20of%20the%20grave%20dangers%20associated%20with%20electoral%20bonds.%20Copies%20of%20communication%20between%20the%20Reserve%20Bank%20of%20India%20and%20the%20finance%20ministry%20obtained%20under%20the%20RTI%20Act%20reveal%20that%20the%20RBI%20warned%20that%20EBs%20will%20violate%20the%20principle%20and%20spirit%20of%20the%20Prevention%20of%20Money%20Laundering%20Act%20(PMLA)%2C%20as%20the%20original%20buyer%20need%20not%20be%20the%20actual%20contributor%20to%20the%20political%20party.%20While%20the%20person%20buying%20the%20bearer%20bond%20will%20need%20to%20fulfil%20KYC%20requirements%2C%20the%20identity%20of%20the%20intervening%20entities%20will%20be%20unknown.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F02081614%2FRBI-1.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F02081614%2FRBI-1.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-conten