on8-2.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20August%202021%2C%20I%20received%20a%20surprise%20e-mail%20from%20eminent%20art%20historian%2C%20professor%20Kavita%20Singh%20of%20Jawaharlal%20Nehru%20University.%20She%20asked%20if%20I%20knew%20of%20a%20magnificent%20illustrated%20manuscript%20of%20the%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3ERamcharitmanas%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3Eof%20Tulsidas%20(1574%20AD)%2C%20the%20popular%20Hindi%20retelling%20of%20the%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3ERamayana%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3Estory%2C%20produced%20for%20the%20Maharaja%20of%20Banaras%20at%20the%20end%20of%20the%2018%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3Eth%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%20century.%20She%20wondered%20whether%20I%20knew%20that%20this%20seven-volume%20work%20was%20now%20being%20%E2%80%9Cdispersed%E2%80%9D%20%E2%80%93%20broken%20up%20and%20sold%2C%20page-by-page%2C%20in%20the%20art%20market.%20Finally%2C%20she%20asked%20if%20I%20would%20assist%20her%20and%20her%20former%20student%20Parul%20Singh%20in%20preparing%20an%20exhibit%20of%20some%20of%20its%20folios%20for%20an%20exciting%20new%20museum%2C%20MAP%20(Museum%20of%20Art%20and%20Photography)%2C%20in%20Bengaluru%2C%20at%20the%20invitation%20of%20its%20founder%2C%20Abhishek%20Poddar.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EI%20had%20indeed%20heard%20of%20this%20legendary%20manuscript%2C%20popularly%20known%20as%20the%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EKanchana%20Chitra%20Ramayana%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E(%E2%80%9CGolden%20Illustrated%20Ramayana%2C%E2%80%9D%20because%20of%20the%20copious%20use%20of%20gold%20in%20its%20production)%2C%20from%20the%20late%20Maharaja%20Vibhuti%20Narayan%20Singh%20(1927-2000)%2C%20when%20I%20interviewed%20him%20in%201982%20during%20my%20research%20on%20oral%20performance%20traditions%20of%20the%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3ERamcharitmanas%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E.%20He%20told%20me%20proudly%20that%20this%20work%2C%20produced%20at%20immense%20cost%20for%20his%20ancestor%20Udit%20Narayan%20Singh%20(reigned%201795-1835)%2C%20was%20one%20of%20the%20treasures%20of%20his%20family.%20Prepared%20by%20a%20veritable%20army%20of%20painters%2C%20calligraphers%2C%20and%20illuminators%20working%20under%20the%20guidance%20of%20revered%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3ERamayanis%20%E2%80%93%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3Etraditional%20scholars%20of%20the%20Tulsidas%20epic%20%E2%80%93%20it%20was%2C%20the%20Raja%20emphasised%2C%20%E2%80%9Cnot%20just%20an%20illustrated%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3ERamayana%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%E2%80%9D%20but%20rather%20a%20%E2%80%9Cvisual%20commentary%E2%80%9D%20(%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3Edrishya%20tika%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E)%20on%20the%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3ERamcharitmanas.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3ENearly%20two%20decades%20later%2C%20when%20I%20accompanied%20a%20television%20crew%20making%20a%20documentary%20on%20the%20legacy%20of%20Tulsidas%20who%20had%20received%20permission%20to%20film%20inside%20the%20Ramnagar%20palace%20library%2C%20I%20was%20permitted%20to%20see%20a%20few%20pages%20from%20one%20of%20the%20seven%20bound%20volumes.%20Now%2C%20after%20another%20two%20decades%2C%20I%20learned%20from%20Kavita%20Singh%20that%20this%20treasure%2C%20hidden%20from%20view%20for%20nearly%20200%20years%2C%20was%20no%20longer%20intact%E2%80%94yet%20paradoxically%2C%20it%20might%20now%20be%20seen%2C%20at%20least%20in%20fragments%2C%20by%20a%20wider%20audience.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F01171048%2FRamnagar.1.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F01171048%2FRamnagar.1.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F01171048%2FRamnagar.1-300x250.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F01171048%2FRamnagar.1-1024x852.jpg%201024w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-682969%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22999%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EThe%20author%20viewing%20a%20volume%20of%20the%20Kanchana%20Chitra%20Ramayana%20in%20Ramnagar%20Fort%2C%201999.%20Photo%3A%20Philip%20Lutgendorf%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EI%20was%20happy%20to%20assist%20in%20the%20project%2C%20albeit%20marginally.%20The%20volumes%20of%20the%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EGolden%20Ramayana%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3Ehad%20been%20vertically%20bound%20like%20modern%20books%2C%20with%20a%20page%20of%20elegant%20Devanagari%20calligraphy%20facing%20each%20large%20and%20sumptuous%20(18.5%C3%9714%20inch)%20painting%20that%20%E2%80%9Ccommented%E2%80%9D%20on%20it%E2%80%94the%20entire%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3ERamcharitmanas%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3Etext%20comprising%20more%20than%20a%20thousand%20pages%20of%20text%20and%20paintings.%20Dispersed%2C%20however%2C%20each%20painting%20stood%20alone%20and%20out%20of%20context%2C%20and%20the%20text%20on%20its%20reverse%20side%20did%20not%20correspond%20to%20it%20but%20rather%20belonged%20to%20what%20would%20have%20been%20the%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3Enext%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3Epainting%20in%20the%20series.%20As%20a%20scholar%20of%20the%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EManas%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20it%20was%20easy%20for%20me%20to%20read%20each%20page%20and%20then%20extrapolate%20backwards%20to%20identify%20the%20text%20%E2%80%93%20usually%20two%20to%20three%20stanzas%20%E2%80%93%20that%20would%20have%20preceded%20it%2C%20and%20thus%20I%20was%20able%20to%20save%20my%20art%20historian%20colleagues%20a%20little%20time%20as%20they%20began%20delving%20into%20the%20complexity%2C%20detail%2C%20and%20nuance%20of%20these%20paintings%20and%20selecting%20and%20ordering%20those%20to%20be%20shown%20at%20MAP.%20And%20as%20it%20turned%20out%2C%20time%20was%20important%3A%20Singh%20was%20undergoing%20treatment%20for%20a%20rare%20and%20aggressive%20cancer%20that%20would%20tragically%20cut%20short%20her%20life%20on%20July%2030%20of%20this%20year%2C%20a%20mere%20month%20and%20a%20half%20before%20the%20opening%20of%20%E2%80%9CThe%20Book%20of%20Gold%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20magnificent%20exhibition%20that%20now%20represents%20the%20fruit%20of%20her%20final%20labour%20and%20on%20which%20she%20worked%20tirelessly%20almost%20to%20her%20last%20breath.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F01170956%2FRCM-MAP_installation10.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F01170956%2FRCM-MAP_installation10.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F01170956%2FRCM-MAP_installation10-300x200.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F01170956%2FRCM-MAP_installation10-1024x683.jpg%201024w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-682968%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22800%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EPhoto%20Courtesy%3A%20MAP%2C%20Bengaluru%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20result%20%E2%80%93%20some%20eighty%20paintings%20gorgeously%20mounted%20in%20two%20large%20galleries%20on%20the%20third%20floor%20of%20MAP%20by%20the%20Museum%E2%80%99s%20talented%20curatorial%20and%20design%20staff%20%E2%80%93%20is%20not%20simply%20a%20dazzling%20and%20beautifully%20documented%20exhibition%20that%20pays%20fitting%20tribute%20to%20its%20principal%20curator.%20It%20is%20also%2C%20as%20Singh%20observes%20in%20her%20writing%20on%20the%20show%2C%20a%20demonstration%20of%20the%20need%20to%20revise%20the%20art-historical%20narrative%20about%20pre-colonial%20painting%20in%20North%20India%2C%20which%20long%20held%20that%20little%20of%20substance%20or%20innovation%20was%20produced%20after%20the%20end%20of%20the%2018th%20century%2C%20especially%20in%20the%20Banaras%20area.%20As%20the%20show%20makes%20clear%2C%20master%20painters%20from%20several%20urban%20%E2%80%9Cschools%E2%80%9D%20%E2%80%93%20probably%20including%20Jaipur%2C%20Delhi%2C%20Lucknow%2C%20Murshidabad%2C%20and%20Datia%20%E2%80%93%20were%20enlisted%20to%20work%20on%20this%20massive%20project%2C%20which%20continued%20for%2018%20years%20(1796-1814).%20Given%20lavish%20resources%2C%20including%20pigments%20of%20gold%20and%20lapis%20lazuli%2C%20by%20a%20patron%20who%20aspired%20to%20surpass%20the%20illuminated%20codices%20of%20the%20Mughals%2C%20and%20guided%20by%20the%20visionary%20input%20of%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3ERamayanis%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3Ewho%20were%20often%20adepts%20of%20the%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3Erasika%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3Eschool%20of%20meditation%2Fvisualisation%2C%20they%20produced%20stunning%20paintings.%20Each%20must%20have%20taken%20weeks%20to%20complete%2C%20teeming%20with%20individualised%20figures%20as%20well%20as%20detailed%20renderings%20of%20costumes%2C%20buildings%2C%20cities%2C%20villages%2C%20and%20landscapes%20dense%20with%20vegetation%2C%20animals%2C%20and%20birds.%20Though%20I%20had%20seen%20impressive%20digital%20scans%20of%20many%20of%20them%2C%20nothing%20prepared%20me%20for%20the%20explosion%20of%20colour%20(on%20pages%20shielded%20from%20light%20for%20nearly%20200%20years%2C%20and%20now%20carefully%20lit%20to%20protect%20their%20pigments)%20and%20the%20almost%20unbelievable%20abundance%20of%20detail%20in%20each%20one.%20In%20the%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EBalakanda%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3Epaintings%20of%20Ram%20and%20Sita%E2%80%99s%20wedding%2C%20for%20example%2C%20the%20rendering%20of%20hundreds%20of%20figures%20includes%20exquisite%20detail%20of%20brocaded%20fabrics%2C%20jewellery%2C%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3Emandaps%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%3C%2Fspan%3E%20%3Cspan%3Eand%20carpets%2C%20within%20architectural%20settings%20that%20evoke%20the%20courtly%20world%20of%20late-18th-century%20Ramnagar%2C%20and%20the%20triumphant%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EUttarkanda%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3Eevocations%20of%20%E2%80%9CRamraj%E2%80%9D%20similarly%20conjure%20a%20utopian%20Banaras%20of%20multi-storied%20houses%20(the%20cutaway%20interiors%20of%20which%20play%20M.C.%20Escher-like%20tricks%20of%20perspective)%2C%20each%20showcasing%20model%20behaviours%20of%20the%20exemplary%20citizens%20of%20Ram%E2%80%99s%20capital.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F01170945%2FRCK-folios-full-HD-97.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22900%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F01170945%2FRCK-folios-full-HD-97.jpg%20900w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F01170945%2FRCK-folios-full-HD-97-225x300.jpg%20225w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F01170945%2FRCK-folios-full-HD-97-768x1024.jpg%20768w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-682967%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EWedding%20Procession%20Prepares%20to%20Leave%20for%20Janakpur%201808%20%7C%20Balakanda%20%7C%20Style%20A%2C%20Workshop%20A%2C%20Artists%20using%20stylistic%20idioms%20from%20Awadh%2C%20Jaipur%20and%20Murshidabad%20%7C%20H.%2048%20x%20W.%2036%20cm%20%7C%20Private%20Collection%20%7C%20Photo%20Courtesy%3A%20MAP%2C%20Bengaluru%20%26amp%3B%20Philippe%20Calia%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F01171143%2Fnew.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22900%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F01171143%2Fnew.jpg%20900w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F01171143%2Fnew-225x300.jpg%20225w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F01171143%2Fnew-768x1024.jpg%20768w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-682970%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3Ehe%20Astrologers%20Set%20the%20Date%20for%20the%20Wedding%201808%20%7C%20Balakanda%20%7C%20Style%20B%2C%20Late-eighteenth%20century%20Delhi%20or%20Lucknow%20%7C%20H.%2047.5%20x%20W.%2035.5%20cm%20%7C%20Rajeev%20Rawat%20Collection%20%7C%20Photo%20Courtesy%3A%20MAP%2C%20Bengaluru%20%26amp%3B%20Philippe%20Calia%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20curators%20have%20wisely%20avoided%20a%20mere%20chronological%20recapitulation%20of%20the%20familiar%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3ERamayana%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3Enarrative%20and%20have%20instead%20grouped%20paintings%20in%20thematic%20sets%2C%20accompanied%20by%20lucid%20documentation%20that%20sets%20the%20%E2%80%9CGolden%20Book%E2%80%9D%20within%20(among%20other%20contexts)%20the%20cultural%20history%20of%20Banaras%20state%2C%20the%20political%20aspirations%20of%20its%20rulers%2C%20the%20idiosyncrasies%20and%20innovations%20of%20Tulsidas%E2%80%99s%20epic%20narrative%2C%20and%20the%20almost%20obsessive%20culture%20of%20religio-aesthetic%20scholasticism%20and%20connoisseurship%20that%20developed%20around%20it.%20The%20paradoxical%20juxtaposition%20of%20themes%20of%20inclusive%2C%20egalitarian%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3Ebhakti%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20and%20Brahman-brokered%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3Evarnashrama-dharma%2C%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3Eso%20evident%20in%20Tulsidas%E2%80%99s%20writing%2C%20is%20likewise%20rightly%20identified%20and%20contextualised.%20Besides%20the%20sheer%20visual%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3Eananda%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20the%20show%20affords%20(and%20I%20spent%20a%20good%20part%20of%20two%20days%20in%20the%20galleries%2C%20often%20gasping%20in%20wonder)%2C%20it%20offers%20the%20attentive%20viewer%20a%20marvellous%20introduction%20to%20one%20of%20the%20great%20classics%20of%20Indian%20literature%20as%20well%20as%20a%20detailed%20picture%20of%20art%20and%20society%20in%20the%20eastern%20Ganga%20valley%20on%20the%20cusp%20of%20colonialism.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAdditionally%2C%20the%20exhibition%20features%20a%20digital%20flip-book%20of%20the%20entire%20seven-volume%20work%20as%20it%20existed%20pre-dispersal.%20This%20record%2C%20so%20rare%20in%20the%20world%20of%20piecemeal%20manuscripts%2C%20exists%20due%20to%20the%20happy%20circumstance%20of%20the%20Maharaja%20having%20consented%2C%20in%201976%2C%20to%20have%20all%20seven%20volumes%20photographed%20by%20the%20Center%20for%20Art%20and%20Archaeology%20of%20the%20American%20Institute%20of%20Indian%20Studies%20(AIIS).%20Protected%20for%20a%20half-century%20in%20the%20Institute%E2%80%99s%20archive%20in%20Gurugram%2C%20these%20images%20were%20recently%20digitised%20and%20made%20available%20to%20Kavita%20Singh%20and%20her%20collaborators%20and%20now%20constitute%20a%20unique%20resource%20for%20further%20study%20of%20this%20masterpiece.%20And%20finally%2C%20yet%20another%20MAP%20gallery%20offers%20a%20display%20by%20brilliant%20digital%2Fvideo%20artist%20Amit%20Dutta%20that%20playfully%20yet%20reverently%20animates%20various%20elements%20from%20the%20paintings%20to%20astonishing%20visual%20effect.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThis%20extravagant%20exhibition%2C%20on%20display%20through%20March%208%202024%2C%20is%20in%20every%20way%20a%20rare%20treat%2C%20for%20it%20is%20extremely%20unlikely%20that%20we%20will%20ever%20again%20be%20able%20to%20see%20so%20much%20of%20the%20fabled%20%E2%80%9CGolden%20Book%2C%E2%80%9D%20superbly%20displayed%20and%20documented%2C%3C%2Fspan%3E%20%3Cspan%3Ein%20one%20place.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%3Cspan%3EPhilip%20Lutgendorf%2C%20Emeritus%20Professor%20of%20Hindi%20and%20Modern%20Indian%20Studies%20at%20the%20University%20of%20Iowa%20is%20the%20author%20of%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fem%3EThe%20Life%20of%20a%20Text%3A%20Performing%20the%20R%C4%81mcaritm%C4%81nas%20of%20Tulsidas%3Cem%3E%3Cspan%3E(1991)%20and%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fem%3EHanuman%E2%80%99s%20Tale%3A%20The%20Messages%20of%20a%20Divine%20Monkey%3Cem%3E%3Cspan%3E(2007).%20His%20seven-volume%20translation%20of%20the%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3Cspan%3ERamcharitmanas%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cem%3E%3Cspan%3Ehas%20appeared%20as%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fem%3EThe%20Epic%20of%20Ram%3Cem%3E%20%3Cspan%3Ein%20the%20Murty%20Classical%20Library%20of%20India%20series%20(2016-2023).%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1698892215000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F01170934%2FRCM-MAP_installation8-2.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fbooks%2Fbengaluru-museum-rare-glimpse-golden-pages-illustrated-ramayana%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Gold%20and%20lapis%20lazuli%20were%20used%20by%20craftsmen%20in%20this%20work%20commissioned%20by%20the%20Maharaja%20of%20Benares%20in%20late%2018th%20and%20early%2019th%20century.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A4%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fbooks%2Fbengaluru-museum-rare-glimpse-golden-pages-illustrated-ramayana%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Palestinian%20Americans%20in%20