20Doctor%20Tricks%20Cancer%20Patient%20Into%20%26quot%3BCement%20Treatment%26quot%3B%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EA%20self-proclaimed%20%26quot%3Btumour%20research%20institute%26quot%3B%20in%20China%20is%20under%20investigation%20after%20a%20woman%20exposed%20how%20her%20cancer-stricken%20mother%20was%20duped%20into%20paying%20a%20staggering%20200%2C000%20yuan%20(approximately%20Rs%2022.76%20lakh)%20for%20treatments%20that%20include%20bloodletting%20and%20even%20applying%20cement%20to%20her%20skin.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.scmp.com%2Fnews%2Fpeople-culture%2Ftrending-china%2Farticle%2F3239279%2Fbloodletting-and-cement-bizarre-breast-cancer-treatment-sparks-probe-fake-china-doctor-who-swindled%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3ESouth%20China%20Morning%20Post%20(SCMP)%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%20woman%2C%20surnamed%20Wang%2C%20learned%20that%20her%20mother%20had%20been%20diagnosed%20with%20late-stage%20breast%20cancer%20at%20the%20end%20of%202021.%20Soon%20after%20diagnosis%2C%20the%20two%20women%20were%20introduced%20to%20a%20traditional%20Chinese%20medicine%20doctor%20in%20Wuhan%2C%20who%20claimed%20to%20specialise%20in%20treating%20cancer.%20They%20travelled%20to%20meet%20the%20man%2C%20surnamed%20Yu%2C%20at%20his%20Dongyusanbao%20Tumour%20Research%20Institute%2C%20where%20he%20told%20them%20he%20had%20invented%20a%20medicine%20that%20could%20kill%20cancer%20cells.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20Ms%20Wang%2C%20Mr%20Yu%20went%20to%20great%20lengths%20to%20convince%20the%20two%20women%2C%20showcasing%20what%20appeared%20to%20be%20credible%20patent%20documents%20and%20prestigious%20awards%20certificates%20for%20his%20cancer%20treatment.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EFilled%20with%20hope%2C%20Ms%20Wang's%20mother%20immediately%20purchased%20the%20first%20batch%20of%20liquid%20medication%20from%20Mr%20Yu%20at%20a%20cost%20of%2020%2C000%20yuan%20(US%242%2C700)%2C%20which%20he%20assured%20was%20a%20simple%20oral%20remedy.%20Over%20the%20course%20of%20a%20year%2C%20Ms%20Wang%20said%20she%20and%20her%20mother%20flew%20to%20Wuhan%20from%20their%20home%20in%20northeastern%20Liaoning%20province%20six%20times.%20This%20journey%20took%20a%20severe%20financial%20toll%2C%20with%20the%20total%20expenditure%20racing%20over%20200%2C000%20yuan.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EMoreover%2C%20in%20addition%20to%20giving%20the%20elderly%20woman%20oral%20medication%2C%20Mr%20Yu%20also%20made%20dozens%20of%20injections%20into%20her%20breasts%20to%20make%20her%20lose%20blood%2C%20Ms%20Wang%20said%2C%20as%20per%20the%20outlet.%20He%20bizarrely%20also%20told%20the%20woman%20to%20apply%20a%20mixture%20of%20cement%20and%20lime%20skin%20under%20her%20armpits%2C%20claiming%20that%20it%20would%20aid%20in%20shrinking%20the%20cancerous%20lumps.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHe%20told%20my%20mother%20to%20apply%20cement%20mixed%20with%20lime%20on%20the%20skin%20under%20her%20armpits%2C%20saying%20this%20could%20help%20shrink%20lumps.%20My%20mother%20followed%20his%20instructions%20but%20her%20skin%20festered%20after%20doing%20it%20for%20two%20months%2C%26quot%3B%20Ms%20Wang%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EAlso%20Read%20%7C%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fus-man-arrested-for-pointing-gun-at-6-year-old-boys-head-over-halloween-candy-bag-4536390%5C%22%3EUS%20Man%20Arrested%20For%20Pointing%20Gun%20At%206-Year-Old%20Boy's%20Head%20Over%20Halloween%20Candy%20Bag%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20in%20April%20this%20year%2C%20Ms%20Wang's%20mother's%20condition%20deteriorated%20and%20local%20doctors%20told%20her%20that%20the%20cancer%20cells%20had%20spread%20across%20her%20body.%20But%20Mr%20Yu%20insisted%20that%20was%20normal%20and%20even%20told%20them%20not%20to%20worry.%20He%20even%20convinced%20the%20woman%20to%20continue%20drinking%20his%20medicine.%20However%2C%20this%20ultimately%20led%20to%20the%20mother's%20death%20in%20June%2C%20Ms%20Wang%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%