20Sanghavi%20said%2C%20leaving%20the%20audience%20in%20splits.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAddressing%20a%20gathering%20of%20industry%20representatives%20and%20investors%2C%20the%20Gujarat%20minister%2C%20who%20holds%20the%20Home%20and%20Industries%20portfolios%2C%20among%20others%2C%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BI%20have%20visited%20several%20parts%20of%20West%20Bengal%20and%20I%20have%20seen%20so%20many%20similarities%20between%20Gujarat%20and%20the%20state.%20Gujarat%20and%20Bengal%20can%20march%20ahead%20together.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EDuring%20the%20interactions%2C%20Mr%20Sanghavi%20shared%20insights%20into%20the%20success%20of%20the%20Vibrant%20Gujarat%20Summit%20and%20emphasised%20that%20Gujarat%20has%20become%20a%20role%20model%20for%20development%20and%20a%20preferred%20investment%20destination%20over%20the%20past%20two%20decades.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHe%20also%20highlighted%20Gujarat's%20cumulative%20FDI%20of%20%2455%20billion%20between%202002%20and%202022%2C%20attributing%20the%20state's%20attractiveness%20to%20its%20policy-driven%20approach%2C%20including%20initiatives%20like%20Gujarat%20Renewable%20Policy%202023%2C%20Atmanirbhar%20Gujarat%20Scheme%202022%2C%20Integrated%20Logistics%20and%20Logistics%20Park%20Policy%202021%2C%20Electric%20Vehicle%20Policy%202021%2C%20Tourism%20Policy%2C%20and%20Textile%20Policy.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EMr%20Sanghavi%20also%20spoke%20of%20Gujarat's%20industrial%20development%2C%20specifically%20highlighting%20special%20investment%20zones%20such%20as%20Gift%20City%2C%20Dholera%2C%20and%20Mandal-Bechraji%2C%20as%20well%20as%20Petrochemicals%20Investment%20Zones%2C%20Dream%20City%2C%20Sanand%20Manufacturing%20Hub%2C%20Logistics%20Park%2C%20Delhi-Mumbai%20Industrial%20Corridor%2C%20and%20Mumbai-Ahmedabad%20High-Speed%20Rail%20to%20stress%20that%20the%20state%20has%20world-class%20infrastructure.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EUrging%20investment%20in%20Gujarat%20and%20encouraging%20active%20participation%20in%20the%20nation's%20developmental%20journey%2C