20were%20released%20on%20Tuesday%2C%20infighting%20in%20the%20party%20has%20come%20to%20the%20fore%20in%20the%20form%20of%20protests%20by%20Congress%20workers%20in%20some%20parts%20of%20the%20state.%20The%20workers%20are%20unhappy%20about%20their%20chosen%20leaders%20being%20denied%20tickets.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20protests%20are%20emerging%20as%20a%20major%20headache%20for%20the%20Congress'%20central%20leadership%20and%20Chief%20Minister%20Ashok%20Gehlot%2C%20who%20has%20said%20that%20it%20is%20not%20possible%20to%20keep%20everyone%20happy%2C%20but%20added%20that%20those%20who%20have%20been%20denied%20tickets%20may%20be%20accommodated%20in%20various%20boards.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20Congress%20has%20declared%20names%20for%20156%20of%20the%20200%20Assembly%20seats%20so%20far%20and%20three%20sticking%20points%20that%20have%20emerged%20are%20ministers%20Shanti%20Dhariwal%20and%20Mahesh%20Joshi%20and%20party%20leader%20Dharmendra%20Rathore.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAll%20three%20had%20been%20issued%20a%20show-cause%20notice%20by%20the%20central%20leadership%20for%20their%20alleged%20rebellion%20ahead%20of%20the%20party's%20presidential%20elections%20last%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EWhen%20Ashok%20Gehlot%20had%20emerged%20as%20one%20of%20the%20main%20contenders%20for%20the%20party%20president's%20post%20and%20it%20was%20later%20said%20that%20he%20would%20have%20to%20give%20up%20the%20chief%20ministership%20of%20Rajasthan%20under%20the%20'one%20man-one%20post%20principle'%2C%20at%20least%2072%20MLAs%20close%20to%20him%20had%20submitted%20their%20resignations%20to%20the%20Assembly%20speaker.%20The%20MLAs%20were%20opposed%20to%20Sachin%20Pilot%20being%20named%20the%20next%20chief%20minister%20and%20had%20cited%20his%202020%20rebellion%20against%20the%20government.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ETicket%20Chances%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20protest%20at%20the%20party's%20headquarters%20in%20Jaipur%20on%20Wednesday%20was%20over%20the%20ticket%20to%20Mahesh%20Joshi%2C%20who%20is%20the%20sitting%20MLA%20for%20the%20Hawamahal%20constituency%2C%20the%20candidate%20for%20which%20has%20not%20even%20been%20declared%20yet.%20With%20Mr%20Joshi%20getting%20the%20high%20command's%20notice%20over%20the%20rebellion%20and%20his%20son%20facing%20a%20rape%20charge%2C%20there%20are%20strong%20indications%20that%20the%20ticket%20may%20go%20to%20the%20party's%20Jaipur%20unit%20president%20RR%20Tiwari.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EMr%20Dhariwal%20is%20seen%20as%20a%20close%20aide%20of%20Mr%20Gehlot%20and%20the%20rebel%20MLAs%20had%20held%20a%20meeting%20at%20his%20residence%20instead%20of%20attending%20the%20Congress%20Legislature%20Party%20meet%20on%20September%2025%2C%202022.%20Mr%20Dhariwal%20had%20also%20allegedly%20said%20that%20Mr%20Gehlot%20was%20the%20%26quot%3Breal%20high%20command%26quot%3B.%20At%20a%20meeting%20of%20the%20Congress%20Central%20Election%20Committee%20last%20month%2C%20former%20party%20president%20Sonia%20Gandhi%20had%20allegedly%20objected%20to%20his%20name%20being%20part%20of%20the%20list%20of%20probables%20and%20had%20reportedly%20asked%20whether%20those%20who%20work%20against%20the%20party%20could%20feature%20in%20such%20a%20list.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ESources%20have%20told%20NDTV%2C%20however%2C%20that%20there%20is%20a%20high%20probability%20of%20Mr%20Dhariwal%20being%20given%20a%20ticket%20to%20avoid%20antagonising%20the%20chief%20minister.%20But%20there%20is%20no%20clarity%20on%20whether%20Dharmendra%20Rathore%20will%20get%20to%20contest.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E'Structural%20Issues'%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20Congress%20had%20played%20safe%20so%20far%20but%20the%20protests%20have%20begun%20after%20names%20were%20announced%20for%20some%20contested%20seats%20on%20Tuesday.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ESpeaking%20to%20NDTV%2C%20political%20strategist%20Amitabh%20Tiwari%20said%20that%20while%20both%20the%20BJP%20and%20the%20Congress%20are%20facing%20problems%20with%20ticket%20distribution%2C%20the%20issue%20is%20bigger%20for%20the%20Congress%20because%20it%20has%20not%20managed%20to%20get%20a%20simple%20majority%20of%20101%20both%20times%20it%20formed%20the%20government%20in%20the%20last%20three%20elections.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BCongress%20faces%20structural%20issues%20in%20Rajasthan...%20There%20are%2054%20seats%20it%20has%20never%20won%20in%20the%20last%20three%20elections.%20They%20need%20to%20win%20101%20of%20146%20seats%20to%20actually%20form%20the%20government%20and%20that%20is%20why%20they%20are%20falling%20short%20-%20sometimes%2096%20(seats)%2C%20sometimes%2099.%20And%20when%20they%20lose%2C%20they%20lose%20big%20because%20their%20stronghold%20seats%20are%20very%20less.%20So%20rebellion%20is%20a%20big%20problem%20for%20the%20Congress%20compared%20to%20the%20BJP%2C%20which%20has%20never%20won%20only%20in%2019%20constituencies%20in%20the%20same%20elections%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EOther%20Factors%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20shadow%20of%20the%20Sachin%20Pilot-Ashok%20Gehlot%20feud%2C%20which%20seems%20to%20have%20simmered%20down%20in%20the%20run-up%20to%20the%20elections%2C%20also%20hangs%20over%20the%20Congress%2C%20but%20what%20works%20in%20the%20party's%20favour%20is%20Mr%20Gehlot's%20clout%20and%20sound%20political%20instincts.%20He%20had%20managed%20to%20win%20over%20the%20support%20of%2012%20independents%20in%202018%20and%20they%20have%20been%20given%20Congress%20tickets%20this%20time.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EMr%20Pilot%20has%2C%20however%2C%20said%20that%20he%20will%20decide%20who%20will%20be%20chief%20minister%20once%20the%20party%20wins%2C%20indicating%20that%20he%20has%20also%20been%20promised%20something.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EMr%20Tiwari%20said%20the%20BJP%20finds%20it%20easier%20to%20drop%20sitting%20MLAs%20and%20even%20replace%20members%20of%20the%20cabinet%20like%20they%20had%20done%20in%20Gujarat%20because%20it%20is%20a%20cadre-based%20party%20aligned%20to%20an%20ideology.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIn%20the%20Congress%2C%20however%2C%20the%20cadre%20in%20any%20Vidhan%20Sabha%20seat%20is%20split%20between%20the%20top%20four%20to%20five%20leaders.%20So%20when%20one%20person%20gets%20the%20ticket%2C%20the%20cadre%20loyal%20to%20the%20other%20leaders%20goes%20silent%20and%20does%20not%2C%20normally%2C%20work%20for%20the%20party%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EMr%20Tiwari%20added%2C%20%26quot%3BWe%20are%20seeing%20issues%20in%20the%20Rajasthan%20BJP%20as%20well%2C%20but%20once%20a%20candidate%20is%20announced%2C%20the%20ideology%20ensures%20that%20a%20relatively%20larger%20number%20of%20workers%20back%20him%20or%20her.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EReacting%20to%20the%20protests%2C%20the%20Congress%20has%20said%20that%20it%20is%20not%20surprising%20that%20a%20party%20in%20power%20is%20seeing%20more%20instances%20of%20candidates%20wanting%20a%20ticket%20and%20being%20unhappy%20when%20it%20is%20denied.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BTickets%20are%20decided%20based%20on%20a%20process%2C%20based%20on%20surveys%20and%20consultations%2C%20and%20that%20takes%20time.%20It%20should%20take%20time.%20It%20is%20natural%20for%20some%20people%20to%20be%20disappointed.%20We%20are%20the%20winning%20party%2C%20just%20look%20at%20how%20much%20fighting%20is%20happening%20in%20the%20losing%20party.%20It%20is%20natural%20for%20there%20to%20be%20some%20anger%20in%20the%20winning%20party%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20senior%20Congress%20leader%20Pawan%20Khera.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1698856860000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-11%2Fb3ocpgsg_ashok-gehlot_625x300_01_November_23.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fseeking-2nd-straight-win-in-rajasthan-congress-faces-infighting-hurdle-4536159%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22After%20the%20fourth%20and%20fifth%20lists%20for%20the%20Rajasthan%20Assembly%20elections%2C%20which%20will%20be%20held%20on%20November%2025%2C%20were%20released%20on%20Tuesday%2C%20infighting%20in%20the%20party%20has%20come%20to%20the%20fore%20in%20the%20form%20of%20protests%20by%20Congress%20workers%20in%20some%20parts%20of%20the%20state%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fseeking-2nd-straight-win-in-rajasthan-congress-faces-infighting-hurdle-4536159%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fseeking-2nd-straight-win-in-rajasthan-congress-faces-infighting-hurdle-4536159%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fseeking-2nd-straight-win-in-rajasthan-congress-faces-infighting-hurdle-4536159%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Mob%20Surrounds%20Police%20Station%20Near%20Manipur%20Chief%20Minister's%20House%2C%20Cops%20Fire%20In%20Air%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20Manipur%20Police%20fired%20several%20rounds%20in%20the%20air%20today%20to%20disperse%20a%20mob%20that%20surrounded%20a%20police%20station%20near%20the%20Chief%20Minister's%20official%20home%20in%20the%20state%20capital%20Imphal.%20Curfew%20has%20been%20reimposed%20in%20the%20city.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1698856260000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-11%2Fkpp064q4_manipur_625x300_01_November_23.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fmob-surrounds-police-station-near-manipur-chief-ministers-house-cops-fire-in-air-4536465%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Manipur%20Police%20fired%20several%20rounds%20in%20the%20air%20today%20to%20disperse%20a%20mob%20that%20surrounded%20a%20police%20station%20near%20the%20Chief%20Minister's%20official%20home%20in%20the%20state%20capital%20Imphal.%20Curfew%20has%20been%20reimposed%20in%20the%20city.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A1%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fmob-surrounds-police-station-near-manipur-chief-ministers-house-cops-fire-in-air-4536465%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fmob-surrounds-police-station-near-manipur-chief-ministers-house-cops-fire-in-air-4536465%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fmob-surrounds-police-station-near-manipur-chief-ministers-house-cops-fire-in-air-4536465%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22No%20Bail%20to%20Sisodia%3A%20SC%20Ignored%20Basic%20Principles%2C%20Questions%20of%20Targeted%20Political%20Persecution%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F01213504%2FFoiG_apaMAEaD14.jpeg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20The%20Supreme%20Court%E2%80%99s%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flaw%2Fsupreme-court-manish-sisodia-bail%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3E%20refusal%20to%20grant%20bail%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20to%20Delhi%E2%80%99s%20former%20deputy%20chief%20minister%20and%20senior%20Aam%20Aadmi%20Party%20(AAP)%20leader%20Manish%20Sisodia%20has%20raised%20questions%20about%20targeted%20political%20persecution%20and%20once%20again%20highlighted%20the%20punitive%20nature%20of%20undertrial%20imprisonment.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESisodia%20is%20accused%20in%20the%20Delhi%20liquor%20excise%20policy%20case%20by%20central%20agencies%20Central%20Bureau%20of%20Investigation%20(CBI)%20and%20Enforcement%20Directorate%20(ED)%20and%20has%20been%20in%20jail%20since%20February%20this%20year.%20He%20is%20facing%20charges%20under%20the%20Prevention%20of%20Corruption%20Act%2C%20the%20Indian%20Penal%20Code%20and%20the%20Prevention%20of%20Money%20Laundering%20Act.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESisodia%20is%20one%20of%20several%20high-profile%20AAP%20leaders%20to%20have%20been%20held%20in%20connection%20with%20the%20case%2C%20in%20what%20opposition%20parties%20have%20referred%20to%20as%20an%20act%20of%20political%20vendetta.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EApart%20from%20Sisodia%2C%20AAP%20leaders%20Sanjay%20Singh%20and%20Satyendar%20Jain%20have%20also%20been%20arrested%20in%20the%20case.%20Delhi%20chief%20minister%20Arvid%20Kejriwal%20has%20been%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fdelhi-liquor-policy-case-ed-summons-arvind-kejriwal-for-questioning-on-november-2%5C%22%3Esummoned%3C%2Fa%3E%20by%20the%20ED%20to%20appear%20before%20it%20on%20Thursday.%20AAP%20says%20the%20summons%20show%20the%20ED%20is%20preparing%20grounds%20to%20arrest%20Kejriwal%20and%20is%20an%20attempt%20by%20the%20BJP%20government%20to%20%E2%80%9Cfinish%E2%80%9D%20the%20party.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EWhat%20the%20court%20said%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOn%20October%2030%2C%20a%20Supreme%20Court%20bench%20of%20Justices%20Sanjiv%20Khanna%20and%20S.V.N.%20Bhatti%20dismissed%20Sisodia%E2%80%99s%20appeal%20against%20a%20Delhi%20high%20court%20order%20denying%20him%20bail.%20The%20court%20also%20said%20that%20since%20the%20prosecution%20had%20assured%20that%20the%20trial%20shall%20be%20concluded%20in%20the%20next%20six%20to%20eight%20months%2C%20Sisodia%20can%20move%20a%20fresh%20bail%20plea%20if%20the%20trial%20is%20%E2%80%9Cprotracted%20and%20proceeds%20at%20a%20snail%E2%80%99s%20pace%20in%20next%20three%20months.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CIn%20view%20of%20the%20assurance%20given%20at%20the%20Bar%20on%20behalf%20of%20the%20prosecution%20that%20they%20shall%20conclude%20the%20trial%20by%20taking%20appropriate%20steps%20within%20next%20six%20to%20eight%20months%2C%20we%20give%20liberty%20to%20the%20appellant%20to%20move%20a%20fresh%20application%20for%20bail%20in%20case%20of%20change%20in%20circumstances%2C%20or%20in%20case%20the%20trial%20is%20protracted%20and%20proceeds%20at%20a%20snail%E2%80%99s%20pace%20in%20next%20three%20months%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmain.sci.gov.in%2Fsupremecourt%2F2023%2F26668%2F26668_2023_3_1501_47839_Judgement_30-Oct-2023.pdf%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Eorder%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20%3Cspan%3Esaid.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CIf%20any%20application%20for%20bail%20is%20filed%20in%20the%20above%20circumstances%2C%20the%20same%20would%20be%20considered%20by%20the%20trial%20court%20on%20merits%20without%20being%20influenced%20by%20the%20dismissal%20of%20the%20earlier%20bail%20application%2C%20including%20the%20present%20judgment.%20Observations%20made%20above%2C%20re.%3A%20right%20to%20speedy%20trial%2C%20will%2C%20however%2C%20be%20taken%20into%20consideration%2C%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9D%20the%20court%20added.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20top%20court%2C%20during%20the%20hearings%2C%3C%2Fspan%3E%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flaw%2Fno-money-has-come-to-manish-sisodia-how-will-you-bring-him-under-pmla-sc-to-ed%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Easked%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20the%20CBI%20and%20ED%20how%20they%20would%20establish%20that%20Sisodia%20laundered%20money%2C%20given%20that%20he%20never%20came%20into%20actual%20physical%20possession%20of%20the%20money.%20The%20court%20also%20observed%20that%20Sisodia%20cannot%20be%20kept%20in%20jail%20%E2%80%9Cad%20infinitum%E2%80%9D%2C%20reported%3C%2Fspan%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.livelaw.in%2Ftop-stories%2Fsupreme-court-manish-sisodia-delhi-excise-policy-scam-240294%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Cem%3ELiveLaw%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EFormer%20Supreme%20Court%20judge%20Madan%20B.%20Lokur%20said%20that%20%E2%80%9Coral%20observations%2C%20though%20important%2C%20need%20not%20form%20the%20basis%20of%20a%20judgment.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9COral%20observations%20made%20by%20any%20court%20are%20primarily%20for%20a%20better%20and%20clearer%20understanding%20of%20the%20case%20and%20the%20submissions%20made%20by%20counsel.%20The%20counsel%20also%20benefits%20since%20the%20line%20of%20questioning%20(and%20observations%20of%20the%20Court)%20may%20give%20an%20indication%20of%20the%20mind%20of%20the%20court.%20Therefore%2C%20oral%20observations%2C%20though%20important%2C%20need%20not%20form%20the%20basis%20of%20a%20judgment.%20I%20wouldn%E2%80%99t%20spend%20too%20much%20time%20on%20the%20oral%20observations%20of%20the%20court%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3E.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F25222448%2FSupreme-Court-1.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F25222448%2FSupreme-Court-1.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F25222448%2FSupreme-Court-1-300x174.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F25222448%2FSupreme-Court-1-1024x595.jpg%201024w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-665108%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22697%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EThe%20Supreme%20Court%20of%20India.%20Photo%3A%20The%20Wire%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3E%E2%80%9CBasic%20principles%20of%20bail%20not%20considered%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHowever%2C%20according%20to%20legal%20experts%2C%20the%20apex%20court%E2%80%99s%20order%20denying%20Sisodia%20bail%20raises%20questions%20nonetheless.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CUnfortunately%2C%20basic%20principles%20regarding%20the%20grant%20of%20bail%20have%20not%20been%20considered%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Lokur.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CFirst%2C%20a%20prima%20facie%20case%20must%20be%20made%20out%20by%20the%20prosecution.%20Here%2C%20the%20court%20believes%20that%20a%20prima%20facie%20case%20is%20made%20out.%20That%E2%80%99s%20a%20matter%20of%20opinion%20and%20deference%20must%20be%20given%20to%20the%20view%20of%20the%20court.%20Then%2C%20the%20gravity%20of%20the%20alleged%20crime.%20The%20court%20has%20distinguished%20this%20case%20from%20other%20cases%20like%20murder%2C%20rape%20and%20so%20on.%20It%20has%20also%20distinguished%20this%20case%20from%20other%20economic%20offences%20like%20defrauding%20hundreds%20or%20thousands%20of%20depositors.%20The%20prima%20facie%20case%20seems%20to%20be%20one%20of%20getting%20a%20kickback%20for%20benefiting%20someone.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20important%20considerations%20for%20grant%20or%20refusal%20of%20bail%20are%3A%20Will%20the%20accused%20abscond%20or%20not%20be%20available%20for%20trial%3F%20The%20court%20has%20not%20considered%20this%20and%20the%20prosecution%20does%20not%20seem%20to%20have%20adverted%20to%20this%20at%20all.%20Will%20the%20accused%20tamper%20with%20the%20evidence%3F%20Again%2C%20bald%20advertence%20by%20the%20prosecution%2C%20without%20any%20supporting%20evidence.%20Will%20the%20accused%20influence%20the%20witnesses%3F%20Bald%20advertence%20by%20the%20prosecution%2C%20without%20any%20supporting%20evidence.%20So%2C%20if%20the%20essential%20ingredients%20have%20been%20very%20vaguely%20adverted%20to%20by%20the%20prosecution%2C%20why%20should%20the%20accused%20be%20denied%20bail%20only%20because%20the%20alleged%20crime%20is%20prima%20facie%20%E2%80%98proved%E2%80%99%3F%20If%20such%20a%20situation%20is%20allowed%20to%20remain%2C%20nobody%20will%20ever%20get%20bail%2C%20unless%20the%20prosecution%20has%20a%20terrible%20case.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EG.%20%3C%2Fspan%3EMohan%20Gopal%2C%20advocate%20in%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20and%20legal%20scholar%2C%20said%20that%20there%20is%20a%20%E2%80%9Chard%20lesson%20to%20be%20learnt%E2%80%9D%20from%20the%20court%E2%80%99s%20denial%20of%20bail%20to%20Sisodia.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20hard%20lesson%20is%20that%20the%20primacy%20and%20preciousness%20of%20individual%20liberty%20as%20a%20human%20value%2C%20quite%20apart%20from%20the%20law%20and%20even%20the%20constitution%2C%20is%20yet%20to%20penetrate%20the%20soul%20of%20our%20judiciary%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20told%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Wire.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CSisodia%20was%20denied%20bail%20only%20on%20the%20ground%20that%20one%20accusation%20against%20him%20tentatively%20appears%20to%20be%20credible.%20The%20state%20has%20been%20given%20months%20more%20to%20keep%20him%20in%20captivity.%20If%20the%20evidence%20against%20him%20on%20one%20serious%20accusation%20is%20available%20and%20appears%20to%20be%20solid%2C%20it%20is%20not%20clear%20why%20the%20apex%20court%20would%20give%20the%20state%20several%20months%20more%20to%20keep%20him%20in%20captivity%20as%20an%20undertrial%20rather%20than%20ask%20the%20state%20to%20complete%20his%20trial%20in%20a%20manner%20of%20days%20on%20the%20charge%20that%20is%20cooked%20and%20ready.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3ENo%20bail%20for%20the%20next%20three%20months%20%E2%80%9Cunusual%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAccording%20to%20Lokur%2C%20the%20lack%20of%20possibility%20of%20bail%20for%20the%20next%20three%20months%20is%20%E2%80%9Cmost%20unusual.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CThis%20is%20most%20unusual%2C%20if%20not%20unprecedented.%20Bail%20is%20being%20treated%20on%20par%20with%20a%20status%20quo%20order%20in%20a%20civil%20suit.%20Trial%20should%20be%20over%20in%20eight%20months%3F%20Absolutely%20impossible.%20Charges%20could%20not%20be%20framed%20in%20one%20CBI%20chargesheet%20for%20almost%20a%20year.%20There%20are%20294%20witnesses%20and%2031%2C000%20pages%20in%20one%20case%2C%20162%20witnesses%20and%2025%2C000%20pages%20in%20another.%20Impossibility%20is%20writ%20large.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20effect%20of%20the%20judgment%20is%20that%20undertrial%20imprisonment%20has%20become%20punitive.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAccording%20to%20Gopal%2C%20the%20judgment%20also%20turns%20a%20blind%20eye%20to%20%E2%80%9Ctargeted%2C%20biased%2C%20political%20persecution.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20second%20hard%20lesson%20learnt%20from%20the%20Sisodia%20judgment%20is%20that%2C%20yet%20again%2C%20the%20apex%20court%20has%20turned%20a%20blind%20eye%20to%20a%20grave%20epidemic%20of%20justice%20sweeping%20across%20the%20country%2C%20which%20is%20a%20threat%20to%20democracy%20and%20liberty%20%E2%80%93%20targeted%2C%20biased%2C%20political%20persecution%20through%20selective%20prosecution%20of%20political%20opponents.%20Across%20the%20country%2C%20governments%20(Union%20and%20state%2C%20regardless%20of%20party%20flags)%20are%20unleashing%20investigative%20agencies%20and%20the%20police%20at%20will%20against%20their%20political%20and%20ideological%20opponents%20and%20turning%20prosecution%20into%20an%20electoral%20strategy.%20Miraculously%2C%20members%20of%20the%20ruling%20dispensation%20hardly%20ever%2C%20if%20at%20all%2C%20come%20into%20the%20crosshairs%20of%20investigators%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CWhile%20police%20and%20prosecutors%20enjoy%20vast%20discretion%20in%20deciding%20who%20they%20may%20pursue%20and%20who%20they%20may%20spare%2C%20it%20is%20illegal%20to%20select%20their%20targets%20on%20constitutionally%20prohibited%20grounds%20such%20as%20their%20party%20affiliation%2C%20ideology%20or%20beliefs.%20The%20illegal%20selection%20of%20accused%20based%20on%20grounds%20prohibited%20by%20the%20constitution%20is%20called%20%E2%80%98selective%20prosecution%E2%80%99.%20When%20the%20choice%20of%20accused%20runs%20afoul%20of%20the%20constitution%2C%20the%20entire%20criminal%20proceeding%20is%20vitiated%2C%20irrespective%20of%20the%20determination%20of%20whether%20the%20accused%20is%20convicted%20or%20acquitted%20on%20the%20charges%20brought%20against%20them.%20The%20theory%20is%20that%20the%20constitution%20cannot%20be%20violated%20to%20uphold%20the%20law%20%E2%80%93%20such%20an%20approach%20would%20spell%20doom%20for%20the%20constitution.%20Our%20judiciary%20needs%20to%20act%20against%20targeted%20biased%20political%20persecution%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20added.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3ECourts%20should%20examine%20ED%E2%80%99s%20actions%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EDelhi-based%20lawyer%20Sarim%20Naved%20said%20the%20summons%20to%20Kejriwal%20merely%20hours%20after%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20order%20may%20legally%20be%20seen%20as%20part%20of%20the%20investigation%2C%20the%20courts%20should%20take%20note%20of%20%E2%80%9Ccoincidences%E2%80%9D%20in%20the%20ED%E2%80%99s%20actions.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CLegally%20it%20has%20to%20be%20seen%20as%20a%20part%20of%20the%20investigation.%20As%20a%20lawyer%2C%20I%20can%20say%20they%20could%20have%20summoned%20%5BKejriwal%5D%20earlier%20also%20but%20they%20seem%20to%20have%20decided%20to%20summon%20him%20now.%20But%20in%20matters%20of%20realpolitik%2C%20a%20lot%20is%20understood%20without%20being%20said.%20This%20kind%20of%20coincidences%20in%20the%20ED%E2%80%99s%20behaviour%2C%20that%20they%20only%20go%20after%20opposition%20politicians%2C%20raids%20only%20happen%20before%20elections%20in%20that%20state%20%E2%80%93%20these%20are%20things%20that%20the%20court%20ought%20to%20really%20take%20into%20consideration%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said%20to%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Wire.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ELast%20week%2C%20Rajasthan%20chief%20minister%20Ashok%20Gehlot%20accused%20the%20BJP-led%20Union%20government%20of%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fgoondagardi-says-ashok-gehlot-as-ed-summons-his-son-raids-rajasthan-congress-chief%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Cem%3Egoondagardi%3C%2Fem%3E%C2%A0(hooliganism)%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20after%20the%20ED%20on%20October%2026%20issued%20summons%20to%20his%20son%20Vaibhav%20Gehlot%20and%20conducted%20raids%20on%20state%20Congress%20chief%20Govind%20Singh%20Dotasra%2C%20just%20weeks%20before%20the%20state%20heads%20to%20elections.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EFormer%20deputy%20chief%20minister%20of%20Rajasthan%20Sachin%20Pilot%20also%20accused%20the%20BJP%20of%20targeting%20Rajasthan%E2%80%99s%20Congress%20leaders%20as%20it%20fears%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fsachin-pilot-defends-rajasthan-state-govt-says-ed-raids-as-bjp-thinks-it-is-losing%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Elosing%20the%20elections.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20classical%20idea%20is%20that%20state%20agencies%20are%20beyond%20any%20doubt%20that%20they%20are%20impartial.%20But%20when%20there%20is%20such%20a%20wealth%20of%20evidence%20that%20they%20are%20in%20fact%20partial%2C%20that%20is%20something%20that%20should%20be%20taken%20into%20account%20by%20courts%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Naved.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9COtherwise%2C%20they%20are%20doing%20a%20great%20disservice%20to%20democracy.%20It%20is%20not%20even%20about%20this%20case.%20But%20procedurally%2C%20why%20should%20anybody%20be%20in%20jail%20pending%20trial%20when%20there%20is%20a%20presumption%20of%20innocence%3F%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CIn%20a%20situation%20where%20I%20think%20it%20is%20now%20beyond%20any%20doubt%20that%20agencies%2C%20especially%20the%20ED%20are%20doing%20the%20government%E2%80%99s%20bidding%2C%20should%20that%20not%20be%20a%20factor%20that%20courts%20should%20have%20in%20mind%20while%20dealing%20with%20ED%20cases%3F%20The%20answer%20is%20yes.%20It%20is%20something%20they%20really%20should%20examine%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20added.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1698855643000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F01213504%2FFoiG_apaMAEaD14.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flaw%2Fmanish-sisodia-bail-sc-denial-questions%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20top%20court%20said%20that%20since%20the%20prosecution%20had%20assured%20that%20the%20trial%20shall%20be%20concluded%20in%20the%20next%20six-eight%20months%2C%20the%20former%20Delhi%20deputy%20chief%20minister%20can%20move%20a%20fresh%20bail%20plea%20if%20the%20trial%20is%20%E2%80%9Cprotracted%20and%20proceeds%20at%20a%20snail%E2%80%99s%20pace%20in%20next%20three%20months.%E2%80%9D%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A38%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flaw%2Fmanish-sisodia-bail-sc-denial-questions%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22World%20Cup%20Points%20Table%3A%20Pakistan's%20Semis%20Chances%20Get%20Boost%20With%20NZ's%20Loss%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWorld%20Cup%202023%20Points%20Table%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EThings%20are%20suddenly%20looking%20slightly%20positive%20for%20the%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Babar%20Azam%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F59905-mohammad-babar-azam-playerprofile%5C%22%3EBabar%20Azam%3C%2Fa%3E-led%20Pakistan%20cricket%20team%20at%20the%20ODI%20Cricket%20World%20Cup%202023.%20After%20losing%20four%20straight%20matches%20at%20the%20marquee%20event%2C%20the%201992%20Cricket%20World%20Cup%20champions%20returned%20to%20winning%20ways%20with%20a%20seven-wicket%20win%20over%20Bangladesh%20in%20Kolkata%20on%20Tuesday.%20The%20win%20catapulted%20them%20to%20the%20fifth%20spot%20with%20three%20wins%20in%20seven%20games.%20And%20now%2C%20they%20have%20more%20good%20news%20with%20New%20Zealand%20losing%20to%20South%20Africa%20in%20a%20Cricket%20World%20Cup%20match%20in%20Pune.%20%3Cstrong%3E(%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Ficc-cricket-world-cup-2023%2Fpo