%20arrested%20for%20allegedly%20pointing%20a%20gun%20at%20a%206-year-old%20boy%20over%20Halloween%20candy.%20According%20to%20%3Cem%3ENBC%20News%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20the%20incident%20occurred%20on%20Saturday%20in%20New%20York.%20Michael%20Yifan%20Wen%20was%20arrested%20and%20charged%20with%20menacing%20and%20second-degree%20endangering%20the%20welfare%20of%20a%20child%2C%20Nassau%20County%20police%20said%20in%20a%20statement.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20incident%20began%20when%20a%20mother%20drove%20her%20daughter%2C%20two%20sons%2C%20and%20a%20nephew%20to%20a%20nearby%20residence%20to%20drop%20off%20a%20goody%20bag.%20Her%2010-year-old%20daughter%20and%206-year-old%20son%20rang%20the%20doorbell%20and%20dropped%20off%20a%20Halloween%20goody%20bag%20on%20the%20porch%20for%20the%20girl's%20friend.%20However%2C%20when%20the%20children%20returned%20to%20the%20car%2C%20the%20girl%20told%20her%20mother%20the%20address%20may%20have%20been%20incorrect%2C%20so%20they%20drove%20back%2C%20and%20the%20boy%20went%20to%20the%20porch%20to%20get%20the%20bag%20full%20of%20candy.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThis%20is%20when%20the%20man%20opened%20the%20door%20and%20pointed%20a%20handgun%20at%20the%20boy's%20head%2C%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nbcnews.com%2Fnews%2Fus-news%2Fman-allegedly-points-gun-6-year-old-left-halloween-goody-bag-wrong-hou-rcna123025%5C%22%3Eoutlet%20%3C%2Fa%3Ereported.%20The%20Nassau%20County%20Police%20Department%20were%20immediately%20notified%20of%20the%20incident%20and%20the%2043-year-old%20suspect%20was%20arrested.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EMr%20Wen's%20attorney%2C%20however%2C%20said%20that%20his%20client%20is%20presumed%20innocent.%20%26quot%3BThese%20are%20just%20allegations%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20lawyer%20said.%20He%20also%20asked%20the%20public%20to%20refrain%20from%20jumping%20to%20conclusions%20%26quot%3Bbefore%20the%20facts%20come%20out%26quot%3B.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fabcnews.go.com%2FUS%2Fma