on%20was%20offset%20by%20the%20increasing%20temporal%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fbusiness%2Findia-business%2Frural-demand-has-started-to-pick-up-consumer-companies%2Farticleshow%2F98745074.cms%3Ffrom%3Dmdr%5C%22%3Erural%20demand%20for%20goods%20and%20services%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20due%20to%20a%20better-performing%20agrarian%20production%20cycle%20when%20monsoons%20were%20better%20on%20average%20and%20more%20workforce%20was%20engaged%20in%20agricultural%20production.%20This%20happened%20especially%20during%20the%20COVID-19%20pandemic.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EDespite%20the%20rural%20economy%20contributing%20temporarily%20on%20the%20consumption%20front%2C%20there%20are%20structural%20issues%20that%20are%20endemic%20to%20rural%20populations.%20These%20range%20from%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bloomberg.com%2Fnews%2Farticles%2F2023-07-03%2Fweak-rural-labor-market-pushes-india-s-jobless-rate-above-8%5C%22%3Ehigh%20rates%20of%20unemployment%20and%20under-employment%20rates%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20higher%20malnutrition%2C%20and%20severe%20infrastructural%20gaps%20that%20hamper%20the%20growth%20and%20development%20of%20the%20rural%20economy%20%3Cspan%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Evis-%C3%A0-vis%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fspan%3E%20the%20urban%20landscape.%20The%20Modi%20government%20has%20tried%20to%20improve%20the%20welfare%20distribution%20system%20of%20public%20goods%20and%20services%20in%20rural%20areas%20through%20different%20centrally%20funded%20schemes%2C%20but%20the%20results%20have%20remained%20mixed%20at%20best.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EHow%20does%20rural%20development%20cater%20to%20macro%20growth%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ERural%20income%20is%20a%20key%20driver%20of%20rural%20demand%2C%20which%20has%20ripple%20effects%20on%20a%20wide%20range%20of%20industries%2C%20including%20fast-moving%20consumer%20goods%20(FMCG)%2C%20automobiles%2C%20housing%2C%20and%20other%20retail%20aspects.%20Increased%20consumer%20spending%20in%20rural%20areas%20fuels%20rural%20demand%2C%20creating%20a%20virtuous%20cycle%20of%20economic%20growth.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAs%20per%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmain.mohfw.gov.in%2Fsites%2Fdefault%2Ffiles%2FNFHS-5_Phase-II_0.pdf%5C%22%3ENational%20Family%20Health%20Survey%20(NFHS)%205%2C%3C%2Fa%3E%20there%20was%20significant%20improvement%20in%20the%20rural%20sector%20during%20the%20survey%20period%20(2019-21)%20compared%20to%20the%20previous%20survey%20between%202015-16.%20The%20quality%20of%20rural%20lives%2C%20ranging%20from%20electricity%20to%20sanitation%20facilities%20has%20improved%20drastically%2C%20leading%20to%20rural%20women%E2%80%99s%20empowerment%20through%20SHGs.%20The%20government%20has%20implemented%20various%20schemes%20for%20rural%20development%20leading%20to%20economic%20growth%20which%20include%20the%20following%20four%20flagship%20programmes%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Col%3E%20%3Cli%3EMahatma%20Gandhi%20National%20Rural%20Employment%20Guarantee%20Scheme%20(MGNREGS)%3C%2Fli%3E%20%3Cli%3EJal%20Jeevan%20Mission%3C%2Fli%3E%20%3Cli%3EPradhan%20Mantri%20Kisan%20Samman%20Nidhi%20(PM-KISAN)%3C%2Fli%3E%20%3C%2Fol%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EMGNREGS%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fharyanarural.gov.in%2Fmahatma-gandhi-national-rural-employment-guarantee-scheme-mgnregs%2F%23%3A~%3Atext%3DThe%2520Government%2520of%2520India%2520passed%2Cto%2520do%2520unskilled%2520manual%2520work.%5C%22%3EMGNREGA%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20passed%20in%20September%202005%2C%20gives%20a%20legal%20guarantee%20of%20100%20days%20of%20wage%20employment%20in%20a%20financial%20year%20to%20adult%20members%20of%20a%20rural%20household%20who%20demand%20employment%20and%20are%20willing%20to%20do%20unskilled%20manual%20work.%20The%20objective%20of%20the%20Act%20is%20to%20enhance%20the%20livelihood%20security%20of%20the%20people%20in%20rural%20areas%20by%20generating%20wage%20employment%20through%20works%20that%20develop%20the%20infrastructure%20base%20of%20that%20area.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EUnder%20MGNREGA%2C%20a%20total%20of%2011.37%20crore%20households%20availed%20of%20employment%20and%20a%20total%20of%20289.24%20crore%20person-days%20employment%20has%20been%20generated%20till%20December%2015%2C%202022.%20A%20total%20of%20289.24%20crore%20person-days%20employment%20had%20been%20generated%20between%20January%202022%20and%20December%202022%2C%20followed%20by%205.38%20crore%20households%20availing%20of%20employment%20between%20April%20and%20December%202022.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20major%20achievements%20of%20MGNREGA%20include%20GIS-based%20Planning%20of%20Gram%20Panchayats%20(GPs)%2C%20National%20Electronic%20Fund%20Management%20System%20(NeFMS)%2FDBT%2C%20Implementation%20of%20Geo-MGNREGA%2C%20Emphasis%20on%20Social%20Audit%20and%20Cluster%20Facilitation%20Project%20(CFP).%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20new%20initiatives%20under%20the%20scheme%20include%20Amrit%20Sarovar%2C%20which%20called%20for%20the%20construction%2Frenovation%20of%20at%20least%2075%20ponds%20in%20each%20district%20of%20the%20country.%20The%20Jaldoot%20app%20measures%20the%20water%20level%20in%20a%20gram%20panchayat%20through%20two%20to%20three%20selected%20open%20wells%20twice%20a%20year%2C%20and%20an%20ombudsperson%20is%20aimed%20at%20smooth%20reporting%20and%20categorisation%20of%20grievances.%20A%20total%20of%20505%20ombudspersons%20have%20been%20appointed.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20984px)%2061vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2045vw%2C%20600px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F31162135%2Fimage-1458.png%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22680%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F31162135%2Fimage-1458.png%20680w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F31162135%2Fimage-1458-300x186.png