and%20adequate%20drinking%20water%20through%20individual%20household%20tap%20connections%20by%202024%20to%20all%20households%20in%20rural%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20programme%20seeks%20to%20implement%20source%20sustainability%20measures%20as%20mandatory%20elements%2C%20such%20as%20recharge%20and%20reuse%20through%20greywater%20management%2C%20water%20conservation%2C%20and%20rainwater%20harvesting.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAs%20of%20October%2019%2C%202023%2C%20the%20Jal%20Jeevan%20Mission%20states%20that%2013.37%20crore%20(69.5%25)%20of%2019.23%20crore%20rural%20households%20have%20household%20tap%20connections.%20It%20also%20states%20that%20all%20rural%20households%20in%20Himachal%20Pradesh%2C%20Punjab%2C%20Haryana%2C%20Gujarat%2C%20Telangana%2C%20and%20Goa%20have%20tap%20water%20connections.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20984px)%2061vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2045vw%2C%20600px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F31165455%2Fimage-1463.png%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22752%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F31165455%2Fimage-1463.png%20752w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F31165455%2Fimage-1463-300x180.png%20300w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-682740%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22452%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EPercentage%20of%20total%20household%20connections%20reported%20in%20July%202023.%20Source%3A%20Infosphere%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20above%20graph%20indicates%20a%20clear%20distinction%20between%20the%20funds%20allocated%20and%20funds%20released%20by%20the%20Union%20government.%20The%20funds%20released%20by%20the%20Union%20government%20are%20lower%20than%20the%20funds%20allocated%20for%20the%20scheme.%20From%202020%2C%20only%20around%2050%25%20of