2C%20(max-width%3A%20984px)%2061vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2045vw%2C%20600px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F31172654%2Fimage-1465.png%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22828%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F31172654%2Fimage-1465.png%20828w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F31172654%2Fimage-1465-300x180.png%20300w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-682751%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22498%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EExtent%20of%20fund%20utilisation%20against%20the%20total%20funds%20available.%20Source%3A%20Infosphere.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cp%3EThis%20graph%20indicates%20the%20percentage%20utilisation%20of%20government%20funds.%20It%20shows%20that%20the%20utilised%20funds%20have%20reduced%20over%20the%20years.%20The%20fund%20utilisation%20has%20reduced%20from%2075%25%20in%202015-16%20to%2061%25%20in%202022-23.%20In%202021-2022%2C%20when%20the%20government%20expenditure%20surged%20significantly%2C%20only%2050%25%20of%20the%20funds%20were%20utilised.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EImplementing%20schemes%20such%20as%20these%20requires%20careful%20planning%20and%20structuring%2C%20which%20is%20often%20overlooked%20by%20states%20to%20achieve%20quick%20results%20that%20have%20long-term%20consequences%20for%20the%20beneficiaries%20of%20these%20schemes%2C%20who%20in%20certain%20instances%20are%20completely%20unaware%20of%20the%20schemes%20in%20the%20first%20place.%20The%20Union%20government%20should%20implement%20a%20stringent%20framework%20to%20assess%20the%20on-ground%20implementation%20of%20these%20schemes%20and%20hold%20accountable%20all%20defaulters%20whose%20aim%20is%20solely%20to%20forge%20numbers.%20We%20discuss%20more%20on%20this%20in%20part%202%20of%20the%20series.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EDeepanshu%20Mohan%20is%20professor%20of%20economics%20and%20director%2C%20CNES.%20Amisha%20Singh%20and%20Aditi%2