sh%20in%20Pune%20on%20October%2019.%20He%20missed%20the%20games%20against%20New%20Zealand%20and%20England%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIndian%20cricket%20team%20captain%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Rohit%20Sharma%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F857-rohit-sharma-playerprofile%5C%22%3ERohit%20Sharma%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20during%20the%20pre-match%20press%20conference%20ahead%20of%20the%20game%20against%20Sri%20Lanka%20in%20Mumbai%20on%20Thursday%2C%20said%20that%20Hardik%20Pandya%20will%20miss%20the%20game%20but%20had%20a%20godd%20news%20also.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BVery%20positive%20development.%20I%20cant's%20call%20it%20rehab%20but%20whatever%20is%20the%20procedure%20that%20he%20and%20the%20NCA%20had%20to%20undertake%2C%20they%20have%20got%20positive%20results.%20He%20is%20not%20available%20for%20next%20match.%20The%20injury%20is%20such%20that%20we%20have%20to%20monitor%20it%20everyday.%20What%20is%20the%20percentage%20of%20recovery%2C%20we%20have%20to%20monitor%20his%20batting%20and%20bowling%20load.%20we%20are%20looking%20at%20World%20Cup%20where%20there%20are%20matches%20every%20three%20to%20four%20day.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3B%3Cem%3EHo%20Sakta%20Hai%2C%20Jaisa%20unka%20chal%20raha%20hai%2C%20jald%20se%20jald%20dekhneka%20mauka%20milega%3C%2Fem%3E%20(Maybe%2C%20the%20good%20progress%20that%20he%20is%20making.%20We%20will%20get%20to%20see%20him%20soon.)%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20a%20report%20by%20news%20agency%20PTI%2C%20star%20India%20all-rounder%20Hardik%20Pandya%2C%20who%20is%20recovering%20from%20an%20ankle%20injury%2C%20is%20unlikely%20to%20return%20to%20action%20before%20the%20team's%20World%20Cup%20match%20against%20the%20Netherlands%20on%20November%2012.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIndia's%20final%20league%20match%20is%20against%20Netherlands%20in%20Bengaluru%20on%20November%2012.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20is%20a%20minor%20tear.%20He%20is%20recovering%20well%20and%20is%20likely%20to