nt%20to%20avoid%20a%20repetition%20of%20this%20situation%2C%E2%80%9D%20Shinde%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EMaking%20an%20appeal%20to%20Jarange%2C%20the%20chief%20minister%20said%20he%20should%20trust%20the%20government's%20efforts.%20%26quot%3BBecause%20of%20some%20violent%20incidents%2C%20the%20common%20man%20should%20not%20have%20any%20safety%20concerns.%20The%20entire%20Maratha%20community%20should%20support%20the%20state%20government%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1698847260000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-11%2Fvsec1ssc_eknath-shinde-devendra-fadnavis-ani_625x300_01_November_23.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fmaratha-reservation-without-touching-existing-quotas-eknath-shinde-4534809%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Maharashtra%20Chief%20Minister%20Eknath%20Shinde%20on%20Wednesday%20said%20the%20all-party%20meeting%20held%20earlier%20in%20the%20day%20decided%20that%20reservation%20should%20be%20given%20to%20the%20Maratha%20community%20without%20tampering%20with%20the%20existing%20quotas%20of%20other%20communities%20in%20the%20state.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fmaratha-reservation-without-touching-existing-quotas-eknath-shinde-4534809%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fmaratha-reservation-without-touching-existing-quotas-eknath-shinde-4534809%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fmaratha-reservation-without-touching-existing-quotas-eknath-shinde-4534809%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Elon%20Musk%20tells%20Sky%20News%20AI%20is%20a%20'risk'%20to%20humanity%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22publishe