red%20as%20a%20kabaddi%20coach%20in%20Chandrapur%2C%20Maharashtra.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20%5Btraditional%5D%20thinking%20is%20that%20boys%20should%20work%20because%20they%20have%20a%20family%20to%20feed%2C%20while%20girls%20are%20expected%20to%20get%20a%20good-looking%20husband%20with%20a%20government%20job.%20But%20my%20brother%20changed%20this%20outlook%20and%20supported%20me%2C%E2%80%9D%20Vidya%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHer%20job%20with%20Magic%20Bus%20inspired%20her%20to%20venture%20even%20further%20outside%20her%20comfort%20zone.%20She%20acquired%20the%20skills%20to%20effectively%20communicate%20with%20school%20principals%20about%20the%20value%20she%20gained%20from%20the%20sports-for-development%20and%20life%20skills%20education%20programmes%20of%20Magic%20Bus%2C%20and%20to%20persuade%20parents%20to%20enroll%20their%20daughters.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CPermission%20from%20parents%20is%20very%20difficult%20at%20times%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20explains.%20%E2%80%9CThey%20feel%20%5Bit%20is%5D%20unsafe.%20It%20was%20very%20difficult%20for%20me%20to%20win%20their%20trust%2C%20but%20I%20did%20it.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EVidya%20was%20one%20of%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F322281%2Fbengaluru-duo-uses-sports-to-help-rural-girls-study-in-school-sportz-village%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esix%20female%20kabaddi%20coaches%3C%2Fa%3E%20from%20similar%20backgrounds%20and%20ages%20(between%2023%20and%2025)%20who%20joined%20Magic%20Bus%20around%20the%20same%20time.%20The%20other%20coaches%20were%20Komal%20Pachare%2C%20Nilam%20Verma%2C%20Shital%20Borkar%2C%20Poornima%20Chandekar%20and%20Reema%20Khushwah%2C%20who%20shared%20a%20common%20goal%20%E2%80%94%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F145074%2Flibrary-books-ruchi-dhona-children-education%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eto%20empower%20girls%3C%2Fa%3E%20through%20sports%2C%20just%20as%20they%20were.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAll%20of%20them%20are%20part%20of%20Magic%20Bus%E2%80%99%20School%20Completion%20and%20Livelihood%20Enablement%20Programme%20in%20Chandrapur.%20The%20purpose%20of%20the%20programme%20is%20to%20train%20teachers%20to%20deliver%20life%20skills%20education%20to%20adolescents%20from%20Class%206%20to%20Class%2010%20in%20collaboration%20with%20the%20government.%20Operating%20in%20Chandrapur%20proved%20to%20be%20a%20success%2C%20leading%20to%20Magic%20Bus%20initiating%20a%20partnership%20with%20the%20government%20to%20further%20expand%20their%20impact.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EMagic%20Bus%2C%20founded%20by%20Matthew%20Spacie%20back%20in%201999%2C%20has%20impacted%20the%20lives%20of%20more%20than%20one%20million%20adolescents%20over%20the%20past%20two-plus%20decades.%20At%20present%203%2C94%2C206%20adolescents%20are%20enrolled%20in%20their%20programmes%20across%202%2C770%20schools.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EReflecting%20on%20the%20initial%20days%2C%20he%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CAbout%2030%20years%20ago%2C%20when%20I%20arrived%20in%20Mumbai%2C%20I%20couldn%E2%80%99t%20ignore%20the%20stark%20contrast%20in%20living%20conditions%20within%20the%20city.%20On%20one%20side%2C%20there%20was%20a%20sizable%20middle-class%20population%2C%20living%20fairly%20ordinary%20lives.%20On%20the%20other%20side%2C%20there%20was%20a%20parallel%20reality%20of%20people%20living%20in%20poor%20conditions.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAs%20an%20outsider%2C%20this%20divide%20deeply%20affected%20me%2C%20compelling%20me%20to%20respond%20in%20some%20way.%20However%2C%20there%20was%20a%20personal%20connection%20that%20played%20a%20significant%20role%20in%20shaping%20my%20vision%20for%20Magic%20Bus.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cfigure%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201280px)%20100vw%2C%201280px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F8_11zon-1698734921.jpeg%5C%22%20width%3