ttps%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F282029%2Frani-rampal-indian-women-hockey-team-olympics-story%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Epersuading%20parents%20to%20let%20their%20daughters%20travel%20%3C%2Fa%3Eout%20of%20their%20district%20to%20participate%20in%20the%20Toofaan%20Games.%20%E2%80%9CIn%20many%20cases%2C%20no%20one%20in%20their%20family%20has%20ever%20traveled%20outside%20the%20district%2C%20never%20sat%20in%20a%20train%2C%20never%20stayed%20in%20a%20hotel.%20For%20them%20to%20imagine%20their%20little%20child%20doing%20all%20these%20things%20is%20very%20difficult%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20sports%20allies%20have%20also%20had%20to%20get%20creative%20to%20conduct%20events%20for%20the%20Toofaan%20Games.%20While%20villages%20have%20a%20lot%20of%20open%20space%2C%20they%20are%20either%20used%20for%20cultivation%20or%20are%20uneven%20and%20covered%20with%20plants%20and%20boulders.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ESo%2C%20they%20sometimes%20enlist%20the%20villagers%20to%20help%20clear%20a%20space%20for%20the%20events%2C%20or%20they%20lay%20down%20tracks%20which%20have%20only%20two%20lanes.%20%E2%80%9CThere%20are%20so%20many%20ways%20in%20which%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F295216%2Fretired-coimbatore-couple-offers-free-education-underprivileged-kids-kalvi-thunai%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ethey%20find%20the%20solutions%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%E2%80%9D%20Singh%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EPersonally%2C%20Singh%20has%20enjoyed%20coaching%20sports%20so%20much%20she%20got%20her%20E%20Level%20Coaching%20Certificate%20from%20AIFF%20(All%20India%20Football%20Federation)%20earlier%20this%20year.%20%E2%80%9CAll%20day%20I%20work%20hard%20in%20the%20office%2C%20but%20in%20my%20mind%2C%20there%20is%20this%20excitement%20that%20I%20must%20finish%20all%20my%20work%20by%205%3A30%20pm%20so%20that%20I%20can%20go%20to%20the%20ground%20and%20play%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%20%E2%80%9CAnoth