%80%9D%20she%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EFurthermore%2C%20the%20orphans%20without%20%E2%80%9Cconnections%E2%80%9D%20were%20housed%20in%20government%20institutions%20that%20lacked%20adequate%20amounts%20of%20food%2C%20medical%20care%2C%20and%20education.%20%E2%80%9CIn%20discussions%20amongst%20people%20and%20other%20NGOs%20about%20the%20orphaned%20children%2C%20I%20kept%20hearing%20that%20nothing%20could%20be%20really%20done%20as%20these%20children%20could%20never%20be%20like%20our%20children%2C%E2%80%9D%20Dr%20Michelle%20says.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CYou%20can%20tell%20me%20you%20don%E2%80%99t%20care%3B%20you%20can%20tell%20me%20it%E2%80%99s%20too%20expensive%3B%20but%20you%20can%E2%80%99t%20tell%20me%20that%20nothing%20can%20be%20done.%20They%20are%20our%20children%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20underscores%20strongly.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%20%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2FDr-Michelle-3-1698418092.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22At%20this%20new%20home%2C%20the%20girls%20shared%20living%20spaces%2C%20recreational%20activities%2C%20and%20got%20education.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2FDr-Michelle-3-1698418092.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2FDr-Michelle-3-1698418092-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2FDr-Michelle-3-1698418092-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2FDr-Michelle-3-1698418092-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2FDr-Michelle-3-1698418092-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-333189%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EAt%20this%20new%20home%2C%20the%20girls%20shared%20living%20spaces%2C%20recreational%20activities%2C%20and%20got%20education.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20bid%20to%20help%20secure%20the%20futures%20of%20these%20girls%2C%20Dr%20Michelle%20started%20her%20orphanage.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3ETheir%20new%20home%3C%2Fh2%3E%20%3Cp%3EA%20year%20after%20its%20inception%2C%20the%20first%2012%20girls%20were%20transferred%20from%20the%20government%20orphanage%20by%20the%20order%20of%20the%20West%20Bengal%20Child%20Welfare%20Committee.%20At%20this%20new%20home%2C%20the%20girls%20shared%20living%20spaces%2C%20recreational%20activities%2C%20and%20got%20education.%20To%20encourage%20the%20girls%20to%20speak%20in%20their%20mother%20tongue%2C%20Dr%20Michelle%20enrolled%20them%20in%20a%20Bengali%20medium%20school.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20didn%E2%80%99t%20start%20introducing%20English%20learning%20until%20Class%205.%20It%20was%20difficult%20to%20find%20teachers%20who%20taught%20them%20seriously.%20After%20several%20years%2C%20and%20the%20girls%20taking%20insults%20from%20the%20teachers%2C%20we%20started%20our%20own%20school%20and%20relied%20on%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F326013%2Fbengaluru-friends-run-gubacchi-non-profit-to-educate-migrant-worker-children-for-free%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ENational%20Institute%20for%20Open%20Schooling%20%3C%2Fa%3E(NIOS)%20for%20the%20board%20exams%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EShe%20also%20established%20a%20smart%20centre%20for%20children%20which%20is%20a%20free%20and%20inclusive%20play%20school%20for%20underprivileged%20children%20aged%20between%202%20and%204%20years%20in%20the%20community.%20The%20school%20includes%20play-based%20and%20activity-based%20learning%2C%20focuses%20on%20the%20development%20of%20social%20skills%20in%20preparation%20for%20formal%20schooling%2C%20and%20a%20nutritious%20snack%2C%20says%20Dr%20Michelle.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20girls%20live%20in%20a%20warm%20and%20loving%20home%2C%20as%20opposed%20to%20a%20sterile%20environment%20that%20often%20embodies%20a%20government%20structure.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAs%20of%20now%2C%20Shishur%20Sevay%20is%20home%20to%2014%20girls%20who%20are%20enrolled%20in%20various%20vocational%20courses%20like%20practising%20different%20forms%20of%20art%2C%20practising%20Yoga%2C%20tailoring%2C%20and%20jewellery-making.%20Of%20the%20total%20girls%2C%20four%20are%20with%20disabilities.%20They%20use%20speech%20generating%20devices%20like%20the%20Tobii-Dynavox%20eye%20tracker%20to%20read%20stories%20to%20the%20children%20in%20the%20school.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%20%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2FDr-Michelle-4-1698418132.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Shishur%20Sevay%20is%20home%20to%2014%20girls%20who%20are%20enrolled%20in%20various%20vocational%20courses.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2FDr-Michelle-4-1698418132.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2FDr-Michelle-4-1698418132-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2FDr-Michelle-4-1698418132-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2FDr-Michelle-4-1698418132-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2FDr-Michelle-4-1698418132-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-333190%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EShishur%20Sevay%20is%20home%20to%2014%20girls%20who%20are%20enrolled%20in%20various%20vocational%20courses.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20device%20is%20designed%20for%20people%20with%20conditions%20such%20as%20cerebral%20palsy%2C%20ALS%2C%20Rett%20syndrome%2C%20aphasia%20or%20spinal%20cord%20injury%20to%20gain%20access%20to%20computers%2C%20to%20communicate%2C%20and%20to%20control%20their%20home%20environment%20with%20just%20their%20eyes.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9COur%20home%20is%20meant%20for%20permanence%2C%20for%20long%20term%20security%2C%20to%20be%20a%20safe%20place%20for%20those%20who%20may%20eventually%20leave%2C%20and%20a%20permanent%20home%20for%20those%20who%20require%20full-time%20care%20due%20to%20their%20disabilities%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20home%20is%20inclusive%2C%20meaning%20there%20are%20no%20separate%20units%20based%20on%20abilities.%20Their%20lives%20matter%20and%20we%20intend%20to%20be%20a%20model%20of%20what%20can%20be%20done.%20Inclusion%20made%20us%20a%20home%2C%20a%20family%2C%20not%20an%20institution%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EOver%20the%20past%2015%20years%2C%20Dr%20Michelle%20has%20faced%20several%20challenges.%20Initially%2C%20she%20had%20to%20fight%20the%20local%20men%20who%20wanted%20a%20key%20to%20the%20home.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThey%20saw%20it%20as%20a%20public%20property%20and%20were%20especially%20angry%20that%20a%20foreigner%20lived%20here.%20There%20were%20rumours%20that%20I%20was%20raising%20the%20girls%20in%20order%20to%20sell%20them%20for%20a%20higher%20price%20abroad.%20I%20was%20given%20death%20threats%20as%20I%20refused%20to%20hire%20people%20working%20under%20a%20political%20umbrella%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20shares.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20was%20warned%20that%20I%20was%20making%20people%20uneasy%20and%20that%20it%20wasn%E2%80%99t%20safe%20for%20me.%20I%20was%20told%20to%20stop%20and%20leave.%20Of%20course%2C%20I%20didn%E2%80%99t.%20Those%20criminals%20were%20why%20I%20was%20here%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EToday%20the%20octogenarian%20says%20that%20there%20is%20no%20o