unces-job-openings-for-scientists-salaries-up-to-rs-79662-per-month%2F%5C%22%3Etechnical%20and%20scientific%20personnel%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20university%20faculty%2C%20researchers%2C%20and%20professionals%20in%20related%20fields.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EThings%20to%20know%3C%2Fh2%3E%20%3Cul%3E%20%3Cli%3EThe%20programme%20covers%20the%20practical%20application%20of%20remote%20sensing%20and%20GIS%20in%20various%20sectors%20%E2%80%94%20including%20agriculture%2C%20forestry%2C%20ecology%2C%20geoscience%2C%20marine%20and%20atmospheric%20sciences%2C%20urban%20and%20regional%20studies%2C%20and%20water%20resources.%3C%2Fli%3E%20%3Cli%3EParticipants%20will%20have%20access%20to%20PDF%20lectures%2C%20recorded%20video%20lectures%2C%20open-source%20software%2C%20and%20demonstration%20handouts%2C%20accessible%20via%20the%20E-CLASS%20and%20ISRO%20Learning%20Management%20System.%3C%2Fli%3E%20%3Cli%3EThere%20are%20a%20total%20of%2010%2C000%20seats%20available%20for%20the%20entire%20comprehensive%20course%2C%20and%205%2C000%20more%20seats%20for%20individual%20modules.%20Additionally%2C%20nodal%20centre%20coordinators%20are%20allocated%2025%20seats%20for%20each%20course.%3C%2Fli%3E%20%3Cli%3EParticipants%20will%20get%20a%20course%20completion%20certificate%20on%20completing%20at%20least%2070%20percent%20of%20the%20total%20session%20hours.%3C%2Fli%3E%20%3C%2Ful%3E%20%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EHow%20to%20apply%3F%3C%2Fh2%3E%20%3Cul%3E%20%3Cli%3EUndergraduate%20and%20postgraduate%20students%20(any%20year)%2C%20technical%20and%20scientific%20staff%20from%20central%20or%20state%20governments%2C%20faculty%20and%20researchers%20from%20universities%20and%20institutions%2C%20and%20other%20professionals%20in%20technical%20and%20scientific%20domains.%3C%2Fli%3E%20%3Cli%3EInterested%20individuals%20can%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Felearning.iirs.gov.in%2Fedusatregistration%2Fstudent%5C%22%2